satellite/000003/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure, likely a bridge or overpass, viewed from above. In the center, a large, flat bridge deck with straight edges and a gray, solid appearance is visible, showing signs of wear and some faint markings. To the upper left, a curved road or pathway runs parallel to the structure, with a few faint light-colored markings. On the right, a section of the structure extends downward, with angled edges and a staircase-like form. The surrounding land is dark and appears to be covered with dense vegetation, giving a shadowy contrast. The image has soft, even lighting, suggesting it was captured during overcast conditions with no strong sunlight or shadows. Overall, the scene feels quiet and empty, with no visible movement or activity.

satellite/000003/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a building complex and surrounding streets. In the center of the image is a modern structure with flat rooftops and what appears to be a raised walkway or patio area. The building has a geometric design and is surrounded by dark patches of trees and undergrowth. To the left, a curved road runs parallel to the building, with cars visible as small shapes moving along it. On the right side of the image, another section of the building is visible, extending outward and featuring more rectangular rooftops. The area appears quiet and empty, with no signs of people. The lighting is even and diffuse, suggesting an overcast day with no direct sunlight. The overall atmosphere is calm and neutral, with muted tones of gray and dark green dominating the scene. The image has a slight haze, indicating light cloud cover or atmospheric opacity. There are no bright colors or dynamic actions, giving the impression of a still, detached moment in a city environment.

satellite/000003/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing a cluster of buildings and roads. In the lower right, there is a large structure with a flat roof and several rectangular sections, possibly a warehouse or a parking garage. To the left and above, a curved road runs through the scene, lined with trees and some smaller buildings. The road appears sparsely used, with only a few visible vehicles. To the left, a dark area suggests a wooded or undeveloped zone. The image has a muted, grayish tone, indicating that the weather is overcast and the light is flat, with no strong shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and slightly barren, reflecting a quiet, possibly industrial or suburban area. The buildings are surrounded by paved surfaces and small patches of greenery, creating a sense of functional design. There are no signs of active human movement, contributing to a still and uneventful scene.

satellite/000004/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure, possibly a dam or a bridge, viewed from above. The central object is a long, stepped concrete wall with a smooth surface and a slight curve, running diagonally through the frame. On the left, there is a smaller, blocky section with two rectangular openings, possibly vents or windows, and on the right, the structure extends into a wider, flat platform. The surface appears weathered, with faint lines and shadows showing texture. The surrounding area is dark and flat, likely a body of water or land covered in dense vegetation, blending into the background. The lighting is dim, suggesting an overcast day with no visible shadows or sunlight. The overall mood is quiet and isolated, with a faint sense of stillness.

satellite/000004/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure, possibly a bridge or an overpass, viewed from above. In the center of the frame, a large, slanted ramp or staircase ascends from a lower platform to a higher level. To the left, a rectangular platform with steps leads downward. This area is surrounded by dark, shadowed surfaces, likely pavement or flat roofing. The right side features a flat, elevated section with a dark rectangular area that may be a window or a vent. The lower right shows part of a sloped roof. On the far left, the edge of a curved road or path is visible, with faint lines indicating lane markings. The image is overcast and flat in lighting, giving it a muted, gray tone. There are no visible people or moving vehicles, contributing to a quiet and still atmosphere. The overall scene appears urban and functional, with no decorative elements. Weather conditions seem to be cloudy or foggy, with no direct sunlight and a lack of shadows. The image has a narrow depth of field, making the immediate structures clear while the background fades into darkness.

satellite/000004/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by roads and greenery. The main structure is a large, rectangular building with a flat roof and multiple wings, giving it an organized, geometric appearance. At the center of the building, a smaller section juts out slightly, possibly serving as a central entrance or atrium. The surrounding area includes several paved roads, with one visible road running vertically along the left side of the frame. Trees and bushes are scattered around the perimeter, adding a natural contrast to the concrete and glass. To the right of the building, a smaller structure with a sloped roof can be seen. The image appears to be taken during the day under overcast skies, as the light is soft and evenly distributed, casting minimal shadows. There are a few vehicles visible on the roads, suggesting light traffic. The overall scene feels calm and orderly, with no signs of activity or motion. The slight angle of the camera from above provides a good view of the layout, highlighting the building’s design and its integration into the surrounding environment.

satellite/000005/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rooftop structure with a flat surface and several rectangular sections connected by narrow walkways. The central object is a large, light-gray roof with two raised platforms on the left side, each marked with white lines. To the right, a smaller elevated section is visible, possibly serving as a mechanical area. Surrounding the rooftop, dark green trees are visible, giving the image a contrast between concrete and nature. The scene is captured under overcast lighting, resulting in muted tones and soft shadows. The atmosphere is quiet and still, with no visible activity or movement. The image feels detached and impersonal, typical of satellite or drone-based urban photography.

satellite/000005/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete industrial or transportation facility. In the center of the frame is a large flat-roofed structure, possibly a warehouse or part of a bridge support, with a smooth gray surface and a few small vertical features that look like vents or conduits. To the left of this central building is a lower, rectangular structure with a similar roof, and to the right, another similar block forms a connected line, suggesting a complex of service buildings. Behind these buildings, a long, straight road or track runs horizontally across the top of the image, possibly a highway or rail line, with faintly visible markings or road signs. Adjacent to the main structures are sections of paved land and what appear to be utility zones or parking areas. The image is captured under cloudy or overcast conditions, with no direct sunlight visible. The overall tone is functional and muted, with a monochromatic palette of grays and dark shadows, giving the scene a quiet, impersonal atmosphere. There are no people, vehicles, or signs of daily activity visible, emphasizing the stillness of the space.

satellite/000005/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by paved areas and roads. The central structure consists of several low-rise buildings connected by flat rooftops and walkways, forming a somewhat geometric layout. To the left, a section appears more enclosed, possibly with partial walls or fencing, while to the right, an open space with a patterned floor suggests a courtyard or plaza. The surrounding roads curve gently, with one visible on the upper left, featuring a single white vehicle that adds a sense of scale. There are no people or moving vehicles, giving the scene a still and quiet feel. The image has a dim, grayish tone, likely due to overcast weather, which casts soft shadows and enhances the stark contrast between the concrete structures and the darker patches of vegetation. Overall, the atmosphere is calm and uneventful, with muted colors and a sense of minimal activity.

satellite/000006/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a building complex with a flat roof and geometric shapes. The main structure is rectangular, with a smaller extension on the left and a curved section on the right. There are several vertical features on the left side, possibly vents or columns, and a flat roof area with some small details. The surrounding area includes paved ground and some open space. The lighting appears balanced, suggesting daytime with clear skies. The image has a neutral tone, with no visible weather conditions like rain, fog, or strong shadows. Overall, the scene feels calm and structured, showing a modern architectural design from above.

satellite/000006/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by paved open spaces. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring a curved extension on the right side that includes a curved glass facade. Several smaller roof sections and rooftop equipment are visible, suggesting the building is used for commercial or institutional purposes. To the left, there is a connected stepped section with a lighter-colored wall, while a tiled courtyard with evenly spaced tiles appears in the foreground on the right. A dark area, possibly a garden or pond, lies along the bottom center of the image. The surrounding area includes roads and a pedestrian crossing at the top right. The scene appears to be captured on an overcast day, with muted lighting and soft shadows. There is no visible human activity, giving the area a calm and still appearance. The overall composition conveys a sense of order and spatial clarity, with clean lines and structured geometry.

satellite/000006/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by roads and greenery. In the center, the building appears to be a modern structure with a flat roof and rectangular sections connected by covered walkways. Its light-colored walls contrast with the darker roof and surrounding dark patches of trees. To the left, a paved area, possibly a parking lot, is visible with a few vehicles parked. On the right, a street with visible lane markings runs parallel to the building, with a pedestrian crosswalk near the top right corner. The area around the complex is mostly shaded, suggesting the photo was taken during a time of day with low sunlight, possibly early morning or late afternoon. The weather is mostly clear, with no visible clouds or rain, casting soft shadows across the structures. The overall atmosphere is calm and quiet, with no visible movement or activity. The image gives a sense of order and stillness, captured from above with a neutral tone and precise detail.

satellite/000007/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building with a curved roof section and a flat extension, set within an urban area. The structure is mostly gray, with parts of the roof showing white, possibly from wear or reflections. To the right, a paved road runs vertically, with faint white lines suggesting lanes, and a few vehicles are visible. On the left, a large empty space lies adjacent to the building, possibly a parking lot or courtyard, bordered by greenery that appears dark and sparse. A pedestrian crossing is at the top right corner of the image. The scene has a calm and somewhat somber atmosphere, with neutral lighting suggesting an overcast day, and the buildings and surroundings appear weathered, giving the place a utilitarian feel.

satellite/000007/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of an urban area, showing a mix of buildings, roads, and open spaces. In the center, there is a large, rectangular structure with a flat roof, possibly an industrial or commercial building, connected to a curved extension on its right side. This main building is situated beside a paved road that runs vertically through the image, with visible lane markings and a pedestrian crosswalk near the top. To the left of the central structure, there is a dark, open area that appears to be a courtyard or parking lot with an indistinct shape. On the right side, a smaller building with a sloped roof is partially visible near the edge of the frame. The image has a slightly grainy quality, suggesting it was taken from a satellite or drone. There are no people or moving vehicles, giving the scene a still and quiet feel. The lighting is even and diffuse, indicating overcast conditions with no direct sunlight. The overall tone is neutral and uneventful, portraying a typical city block without any strong visual focus.

satellite/000007/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a large building complex. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, possibly a school or administrative building, located toward the middle-left of the frame. To the right of this building, a paved road runs vertically, and a crosswalk is visible near the top, indicating pedestrian access. In the upper left corner, another roadway has a white vehicle visible. Surrounding the main building are several smaller structures and open spaces covered in dark green, possibly trees or shrubs, providing a contrast to the gray concrete and pavement. The layout is neat and functional, with clearly defined pathways and sections. The image captures a quiet moment, with no people or moving vehicles visible, suggesting a calm, orderly environment. The lighting is bright and even, indicating a clear day with no visible clouds or fog. The overall tone is neutral and orderly, reflecting an organized urban landscape.

satellite/000008/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing buildings and streets from above. In the center, a paved road runs vertically, with white lines marking lanes and crosswalks at both ends. To the left, a large building with a curved section on its side appears to be made of concrete, its flat roof and rectangular structure giving it a functional look. On the right, another building with a stepped design stands out, its dark roof and geometric shape contrasting with the surrounding structures. Trees and greenery are scattered near the buildings, adding subtle color to the otherwise gray and black scene. The image has a neutral tone, captured in daylight without strong shadows or evident weather conditions, giving it a calm and orderly appearance.

satellite/000008/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection with surrounding buildings. In the center, a paved road runs vertically, marked with a crosswalk at the top and a white line dividing traffic lanes. A small white vehicle is visible on the road near the bottom. To the left, a large building with a flat roof and a curved section protrudes into the frame; it appears weathered and is surrounded by patches of dark greenery. To the right, a modern structure with a rectangular shape and horizontal lines on its facade shows a clean, deliberate design. The area between the buildings features paved ground and some low walls. The scene is captured under flat, overcast lighting, giving the image a muted and shadowless look. There are no signs of people or movement, creating a still and isolated atmosphere. The overall tone is calm and detached, emphasizing the geometric layout of the city rather than human activity.

satellite/000008/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban intersection with surrounding buildings and a paved road. In the center, a crosswalk crosses the road, leading to a small sidewalk and a curb. To the left, a low-rise building with a flat roof and a curved entrance stands beside some greenery and a parked white vehicle. On the right, a larger structure with a modern design and a flat roof dominates the view, featuring a patterned roof surface and a side wall with vertical elements that suggest solar panels or decorative features. The area around the buildings appears mostly empty, with no visible people or heavy traffic, giving it a calm and still feel. The lighting is even and natural, indicating a full daylight scene, likely midday with no clouds blocking the sun. Shadows are soft and consistent, suggesting clear weather. Overall, the image captures a peaceful moment in a built environment, where architecture and infrastructure blend in a structured, orderly way.

satellite/000009/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings and roads. In the center, a long straight road runs vertically, bordered by a modern building on the right with a flat roof and rectangular shape. On the left, a curved section of a structure is visible, possibly part of a parking area or another building with a sloped roof. The surrounding space includes paved surfaces and patches of greenery, likely trees or shrubs, with a few visible cars on the road. There is no visible rain or fog, and the lighting appears even, suggesting an overcast day. The scene feels calm and orderly, with a sense of structure and function, typical of a city block. The image is clear but not bright, giving it a neutral and slightly subdued tone.

satellite/000009/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with buildings and streets. In the center, a dark, rectangular building with a flat roof stands out, showing a pattern of small windows or panels arranged in neat rows. To the left of this building, there is another structure with a curved corner and a lighter-colored roof, possibly a parking garage or a public facility, connected by a walkway. Above these buildings, a crosswalk stretches across a road, with white lines marking the pedestrian path. The surrounding area appears quiet and empty, with no people or vehicles visible. The image has a muted, grayish tone, suggesting overcast weather, and the shadows are soft, indicating either early morning or late afternoon light. The overall scene feels still and calm, with no signs of activity. The texture of the surfaces—roads, rooftops, and sidewalks—adds to the sense of a typical city layout captured from above.

satellite/000009/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, showing a street intersection with two crosswalks. The central focus is a broad road running vertically down the image, marked by two white-striped crosswalks at the top. On the left side of the street, there is an open area with a concrete pavement and a curved structure, along with parked vehicles and a few small buildings. To the right, a large complex of buildings with flat rooftops dominates the view, including a long rectangular building with solar panels on its roof. This section also features open spaces, smaller structures, and patches of greenery between the buildings. The scene has a calm and still atmosphere, with no visible people or traffic. The image appears to be taken during daylight under overcast conditions, giving the view a flat, muted tone. There are no strong shadows, indicating soft and diffused light. The overall impression is one of functional urban planning, with clean lines and organized spaces.

satellite/000010/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with flat roofs and rectangular structures. The central object is a large rectangular building with a dark roof, surrounded by smaller structures and open spaces. To the left, a paved road runs vertically, with a few parked vehicles visible. On the right, another building with a lighter-colored roof extends outward. The area appears organized, with wide walkways and landscaped sections separating the structures. The image is taken on a clear day, with even lighting and no visible shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with minimal activity or movement. A few trees and patches of greenery add small details to the urban landscape.

satellite/000010/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, likely captured during daylight with clear weather and no visible precipitation. The central object is a large, dark-colored building with a flat roof and several rectangular sections, suggesting it might be a commercial or public facility. To the left of the building, a wide road runs vertically, marked with a crosswalk and a few vehicles, indicating some level of traffic activity. On the right, a lighter-colored structure with a sloped roof and a balcony is visible, possibly a residential unit or an extension of the main building. In the background, open spaces appear dark and empty, surrounded by pavement and sparse greenery. The overall scene has a calm and orderly atmosphere, without any signs of crowds or movement. The imaging quality is sharp, with a high contrast between the built environment and the surrounding surfaces. There are no visible clouds or weather disturbances, and the lighting appears consistent, suggesting it was taken around midday. The image conveys a sense of routine urban life, with distinct architectural forms and well-defined infrastructure.

satellite/000010/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a large building complex. The central object is a multi-story structure with a dark, flat roof that has sections of white railing and a small elevated platform on the right side. It sits beside a wide road with a crosswalk and traffic island. To the left, there’s a curved sidewalk and a paved area with trees. On the right of the building, a smaller section with balconies and railings can be seen. The scene has a quiet and empty atmosphere, with no people or vehicles visible. The sky appears overcast, casting a grayish tone over the landscape and creating a uniformly shadowed view. The overall impression is one of a still, somewhat lifeless urban environment, where the textures of concrete, pavement, and dark rooftops dominate the scene. Implementation details are subtle, with no dramatic lighting or color contrast.

satellite/000011/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern residential building with a flat roof and geometric structure. The central object is a multi-level house with dark-colored walls and white trim outlining its edges and railings. On the right side, a balcony area has a large black object, possibly a satellite dish or patio furniture. To the left, another section of the building features recessed areas and multiple square windows. A narrow, light-colored walkway leads to the entrance, which is partially visible at the bottom. The surrounding area appears dark and shadowy, suggesting low daylight. The sky is not visible, but the image has a neutral, somewhat gray tone, indicating overcast weather. The scene looks calm and quiet, with no people or moving vehicles visible.

satellite/000011/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by paved areas. The central structure is large and rectangular, with a flat roof that has sections of dark panels, possibly solar panels, and several rooftop features like vents and small platforms. The building has a geometric design, with multiple levels and protruding sections creating a stepped appearance. To the left, there is a parking lot with a visible row of white lines and a few parked vehicles. On the right side, there is a covered walkway with a white railing, leading to another part of the structure or a separate building. A trailer or large vehicle is seen near the walkway area. The surrounding ground is mostly flat and light-colored, with some darker patches that could be shadows or wet surfaces. The overall scene is devoid of people, giving it a still and quiet feel. The lighting suggests an overcast day, with soft shadows and no strong sunlight. The image has a muted color palette, dominated by grays and dark tones, which contributes to a calm but slightly sterile atmosphere. There is no visible rain or fog, but the sky, though not directly visible, appears cloudy.

satellite/000011/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban building complex. The central object is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof, surrounded by smaller buildings and walkways. On the right side of the complex, there is an open area with a low wall and a few dark shapes that may be vehicles or equipment. To the left, a paved lot contains multiple parking spaces marked with white lines. The area is not crowded, giving it a calm and orderly feel. The image appears to have been taken on an overcast day, with muted tones and soft shadows indicating diffused sunlight. The surrounding greenery is minimal, consisting of small trees and landscaping near the building edges. There are no people visible, which adds to the quiet and still atmosphere of the scene. The overall impression is of a functional and well-planned space, possibly a commercial or educational facility, captured in a moment of calm during daylight.

satellite/000012/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a parking structure with multiple levels. In the center, a large, dark parking garage has several wide, open ramps that connect each floor. The structure is made of concrete and features a flat roof with a few small windows and vents. On the right side, a long white railing runs along the edge of a raised platform, where a large oval-shaped dark object—likely a piece of machinery or equipment—is visible. To the left of the garage, there is a darker area that appears to be a shadowed space or an adjacent building. The ground floor has a small open area with a few bushes or plants along the sides. The lighting is even and neutral, suggesting an overcast day with no direct sunlight. The image has a quiet, functional atmosphere, and the overall scene appears calm and unoccupied.

satellite/000012/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural complex, viewed from above on a clear day with bright sunlight illuminating the scene. At the center, a large structure features a flat roof with a white safety railing, and a dark object, possibly a water tank or mechanical unit, is visible on top. To the left, a lower rectangular building with a darker roof extends horizontally, showing a grid-like pattern of windows or panels. On the right, another section of the complex slopes downward, connected laterally by a covered walkway. Below, a paved area includes several curved plant beds with patches of greenery, indicating landscaping. The surrounding ground is light-colored concrete or stone, with slight shadows cast by the buildings, suggesting midday. The overall design appears clean and functional, with sharp lines and open spaces. There is no movement or activity visible, giving the image a still and orderly atmosphere. The uniform lighting enhances the contrast between light and shadow, highlighting the geometric layout of the site. The scene is calm but not lively, reflecting a quiet urban or institutional setting.

satellite/000012/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex. In the center, a large structure with a flat roof and white railings sits prominently, surrounded by smaller buildings and paved areas. On the left side, a long rectangular building with multiple windows appears connected to the main structure by a walkway. To the right, another building has a more vertical shape, featuring two large air conditioning units on the roof. The grounds are mostly concrete or asphalt surfaces, with some small green spaces and trees visible at the bottom, creating a contrast with the harsh lines of the architecture. There are no people or vehicles visible, giving the scene a still and quiet feel. The image appears to be taken during daylight with clear weather, though the colors are muted and somewhat gray, suggesting an overcast sky or high contrast in the photograph. The overall atmosphere is one of order and function, typical of a commercial or institutional campus.

satellite/000013/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a complex building structure with multiple levels. In the center, a long elevated walkway or bridge connects two sections, supported by beams. On the right side, there are several square air conditioning units mounted on the roof. Large flat areas with open spaces and possible loading docks are visible below the bridge. The building has a geometric design with clear lines and rectangular shapes. The top part of the image is dark, possibly indicating shadows or a night setting. The overall scene is quiet and still, with a gray tone. The weather appears clear, with no fog or rain. The image gives a calm impression, like a silent urban area viewed from above.

satellite/000013/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a prominent building complex. The central structure features a long, rectangular roof with a white railing along the edge, and a large dark shape, possibly a vehicle or equipment, is visible on the rooftop. To the right of this building, a taller section includes a wall with circular and square patterns, possibly ventilation units or solar panels. On the left, another section of the building has a flat roof with what appears to be a small enclosed area or skylight. The surrounding ground is paved with concrete, showing geometric shapes and mild curves, indicating walkways or parking spaces. A dark body of water or large basin is visible behind the main structure, and scattered greenery, like trees or bushes, is present in the lower part of the image. The lighting appears neutral, suggesting an overcast day, with no strong shadows or bright sunlight. The overall impression is one of quiet functionality, with clean lines and organized design. The image has a muted and calm atmosphere, typical of a daytime urban scene captured from above without human activity.

satellite/000013/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial or commercial building complex surrounded by low-density structures. The central object is a multi-level building with a flat roof, featuring a mix of rectangular sections and elevated walkways, including a covered bridge-like structure connecting different parts. On the roof, there are several units that appear to be ventilation or HVAC systems, and there is a flat open area with some equipment visible. To the left, there is a large parking lot with marked spaces, mostly empty, and a few smaller buildings are scattered around. On the right, there is a fenced area with a small rectangular structure and some greenery. The surrounding area includes paved roads and patches of trees, creating a sense of order and function. The image is taken on a clear day, with consistent lighting and no visible shadows, suggesting midday. The overall atmosphere is calm and utilitarian, with a focus on practical design and operational efficiency. There is no sign of people or vehicles, adding to the quiet and static feel of the scene.

satellite/000014/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an industrial or commercial complex with a focus on a large building and associated structures. In the center of the image is a tall rectangular structure with air conditioning units on the roof, possibly a courtyard or utility area detailed with grates and panels. A long elevated walkway extends horizontally from the left, connecting to the building and featuring a curved section near the end. On the right side, a smaller wing of the building contains what appears to be a parking area with vehicles. The surrounding ground is partially paved and has patches of greenery. The sky is overcast, and the lighting is flat and uniform, giving the scene a neutral, functional appearance without strong shadows or highlights. The overall atmosphere is calm and utilitarian, lacking any sense of human activity or energy.

satellite/000014/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by landscaped grounds. The central object is a multi-story structure with a flat roof, featuring several rooftop units that appear to be HVAC systems or ventilation equipment. A long, narrow bridge or walkway extends from the main building, connecting it to a lower section on the left. On the right side, a smaller rectangular structure with a sloped roof stands adjacent to the main building. The area around the buildings includes paved walkways, broken by patches of greenery and small trees. A large, dark body of water lies to the left of the complex, reflecting the overcast sky above. The lighting is even and diffused, suggesting a cloudy day with no direct sunlight. The overall scene has a calm, organized appearance, with clean lines and structured geometry. There is little motion or activity visible, creating a quiet, almost sterile atmosphere. The image feels detached and technical, typical of satellite or drone imaging on a still day.

satellite/000014/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by paved areas and sparse vegetation. The main structure is a multi-level facility with a flat roof, featuring a rectangular section with a central courtyard covered by a glass or transparent material. On the roof of this area, there is a cluster of mechanical units, including two large air conditioning systems. To the right of the building, a paved courtyard with low walls and some greenery is visible, leading to a street with a pedestrian crossing marked by white stripes. To the left of the main building, there is an open space with a few small, irregularly shaped green areas and a covered walkway. The surrounding area has wide, flat surfaces, likely parking or loading zones, with some scattered trees and bushes. The image is taken under clear weather conditions with consistent lighting, indicating a daytime capture. The scene appears orderly but lacks activity, giving it a calm and somewhat empty atmosphere.

satellite/000015/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by land and paved areas. In the center, a rectangular building with a flat roof stands out, featuring visible air conditioning units and a section that appears to be a solar panel array. To the left, a long elevated walkway or bridge stretches across the frame, connecting parts of the structure. On the right, a parking lot with marked spaces and a few scattered trees is visible along a road. In the lower part of the image, curved pathways and green patches suggest landscaped areas. The light is flat and even, indicating an overcast day, with no strong shadows or bright highlights. The scene feels orderly and functional, with no visible people or movement, giving it a calm and quiet appearance.

satellite/000015/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, captured on a clear day with bright sunlight. At the center is a building with a rectangular shape and a flat roof, featuring two large circular structures on top and a smaller enclosed section below. To the left, a long elevated structure with white railings crosses over open space, possibly a walkway or bridge. This structure connects to another part of the complex below. Surrounding the central building are paved surfaces, patches of greenery including small trees and shrubs, and a network of roads. A diagonal road cuts through the right side, marked with white lines. The scene feels organized and functional, with no visible people or vehicles. The contrast between the dark roofs, light-colored pavement, and green vegetation creates a structured appearance. The overall impression is one of calm urban order, typical of a planned public or institutional site. The lighting is even, suggesting the photo was taken midday.

satellite/000015/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a multi-story building with a modern design. The central object is a rectangular structure with a flat roof, featuring a square area with two large circular elements, possibly air conditioning units. The building has a light-colored exterior and is surrounded by a paved ground with trees and some greenery. To the left, a long elevated walkway runs parallel to the building, with railings along its edge. The right side of the image shows a street with a crosswalk and a few parked vehicles, indicating a quiet urban environment. In the bottom region, there are distinct patterns in the pavement, suggesting a structured parking lot or open plaza area. The sky is clear, and the lighting is bright, giving the scene a sharp and clean appearance. No people are visible, and the overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, characteristic of a modern city area. The image captures a moment of stillness, with minimal movement, conveying a sense of routine and quiet efficiency.

satellite/000016/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a mix of buildings and open spaces. On the left, a large rectangular building with a flat roof has several circular features, possibly air conditioning units, and multiple windows. Adjacent to it, a narrow open lot with patches of grass and dirt lies between structures. To the right, a paved road runs vertically, bordered by sidewalks and some greenery. Smaller buildings are visible along the edges, and a few trees are scattered across the scene. The image appears to be taken during overcast conditions, with soft shadows and a grayish tone. The overall atmosphere is quiet and unpopulated, with no visible people or vehicles. The image has a neutral and slightly subdued look due to the lighting and perspective.

satellite/000016/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area, showing a section of a city with buildings, roads, and green spaces. At the center of the image is a rectangular building with a flat roof, which has several air conditioning units and a grid-like structure on its top. To the left of this building, there is a larger structure with a flat roof and many windows, possibly a commercial or office building. A paved road runs vertically through the right side of the image, with a crosswalk at the top and a few parked vehicles visible. Around the buildings, there are patches of greenery, including trees and small bushes. On the right side, a fence and a smaller building are seen, partially in shadow. The image appears to be taken on a clear day, with consistent lighting and minimal shadows, suggesting midday conditions. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no signs of movement or activity. The layout reflects a typical city block, balanced between built structures and small natural elements.

satellite/000016/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area, showing a mix of buildings and streets. In the center, a large building with a flat roof is visible, featuring multiple air conditioning units on top. To the left, a long, low structure with a covered walkway runs parallel to the main building. The building has a grid-like pattern of windows and a central patio area with some greenery. Surrounding the buildings are paved roads and parking spaces, with a crosswalk clearly marked on one street. To the right, other structures with different shapes and sizes are scattered, some appearing more commercial. The area is mostly made of concrete and asphalt, with patches of trees and shrubs adding small green spots. The view is taken from high above, under clear skies with no visible clouds or rain. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting the photo was captured during the day. The overall scene feels organized and functional, typical of a city environment. The grey tones and geometric shapes give it a practical, unemotional atmosphere.

satellite/000017/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block showing buildings, a narrow road, and some green areas. On the left, a structure with a flat roof and air conditioning units is visible, with a small patio and steps leading down. To its right, a dark path runs vertically beside a light-colored sidewalk. A few trees are scattered along the path, and a cluster of darker, dense greenery appears at the bottom center. A round roofed part of another building is seen in the lower right corner. On the far right, a white fence and balcony on a building are visible. The area appears quiet and still, with no people or vehicles in sight. The image is clear, taken during daylight, with natural lighting and no signs of fog or rain. The colors are mostly gray, black, and green, giving a muted, urban feel.

satellite/000017/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a portion of a campus or institutional complex, captured under overcast skies that lend the scene a muted and gray tone. In the center stands a large rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring several air conditioning units and a small open area that appears to be a courtyard. To the left of this main structure is a walkway with a railing, possibly a pedestrian bridge or elevated pathway, connecting to another part of the complex. On the far left, a series of lower buildings with sloped roofs are partially visible, surrounded by paved pathways and sparse greenery. To the right, a wide paved road runs vertically, with a smaller structure and patches of trees or shrubs nearby. The overall atmosphere is quiet and orderly, with no visible people or moving vehicles, suggesting a calm moment in a structured, urban environment. The shaded surfaces and soft lighting suggest a cloudy day, with no direct sunlight.

satellite/000017/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with a mix of buildings and paved areas. In the center-left, there is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring two small, square structures on top, possibly cooling units or small towers. The building has a section with large windows and a covered walkway at the front. To the right of the building, a wide street runs vertically down the image, lined with trees and surrounded by smaller structures. On the right side, there are several buildings with flat roofs and green areas between them. A circular, light-colored building appears in the bottom-right corner, possibly a small pavilion or shelter with a dome-like roof. The overall scene shows a layout of urban development with clear division between built spaces and greenery. The image is taken under overcast conditions, giving it a gray, muted appearance without shadows, suggesting a dull and quiet day. The streets and paths are mostly empty, with only a few vehicles visible, adding to the calm and still atmosphere of the area.

satellite/000018/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a clear, detailed view of a building and its surroundings. At the center is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring a series of air conditioning units and possibly a rooftop garden or platform. To the left, a paved walkway with railings connects to the building, and a curved, landscaped area with small trees and shrubs sits below. In the lower section, a wide pathway or plaza runs horizontally, lined with evenly spaced trees and possibly benches. To the right, a road runs parallel to the building, separated by a sidewalk and greenery. The image is well-lit with no signs of rain or fog, suggesting a clear day. The overall atmosphere is orderly and functional, typical of a city environment.

satellite/000018/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a large building with a rectangular shape and a flat roof. The central structure has a grid-like pattern of windows and a small outdoor area on the roof with two air conditioning units. To the left of the building, there is a wide walkway or bridge with railings, connecting to a lower section of the complex. Below the bridge, there are a few outlined spaces that appear to be parking spots or small gardens, with a few trees scattered around. On the right side of the image, a street runs vertically with a few parked cars visible. There’s a patterned surface near the bottom, likely a plaza or courtyard with geometric tiles. The surrounding area looks mostly empty and quiet, with no people visible. The image is dimly lit, suggesting it might have been taken during early morning or late afternoon. The overall tone is calm and orderly, showing a structured urban environment. The details are clear, but the color palette is muted, giving the scene a somewhat gray and overcast feel.

satellite/000018/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a prominent building with a flat roof and visible mechanical equipment. The central structure stands out with its rectangular shape and grid-like design, surrounded by paved walkways and landscaped green spaces containing shrubs and small trees. To the left of the building, a long elevated walkway stretches horizontally, supported by columns and connected to other parts of the complex. On the right side, a tree-lined street runs vertically, with parked cars and a sidewalk visible. The scene is captured on a clear day with bright sunlight casting sharp shadows, highlighting the textures of the pavement and foliage. The overall layout suggests a well-planned environment, likely a commercial or institutional complex. The simplicity of the design, combined with the clean lines and open spaces, gives the area a calm and organized appearance. The surrounding greenery adds a touch of nature to the urban setting, creating a balanced mix of functionality and aesthetics. The absence of people in the image contributes to a quiet and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/000019/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with a flat roof and surrounding paved areas. In the center, a large rectangular structure has a set of air conditioning units on the roof, and a walkway extends across the top, connecting to a smaller section on the left. To the left of the main building, there is an open space with a few dark patches that look like small trees or shrubs. On the right, a narrow passageway leads between the buildings, bordered by walls and more greenery. The lighting is neutral, suggesting an overcast day, with no strong shadows. The overall scene appears organized and quiet, with no signs of people or activity. The perspective gives a calm, almost detached view of the urban landscape.

satellite/000019/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban structure, likely a building complex with outdoor areas. In the center of the image is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring four visible air conditioning units on the top right section. To the left of the main building, a long elevated walkway with a white railing spans horizontally, connecting different levels of the structure. Below the walkway and along the lower portion of the image, there is a paved open space with geometric patterns and a few small green patches, possibly designed as landscaping. On the right side, a small garden area with trees and shrubs adds a touch of nature to the scene. The overall view is clear and well-lit, suggesting a sunny day with no clouds visible. The image has a neutral and functional tone, capturing the clean lines and organized layout of an urban development. The surrounding area appears calm and ordered, with no visible people or vehicles, giving the impression of a quiet moment in a structured environment.

satellite/000019/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban structure, likely a public or institutional building complex. At the center of the image is a large, rectangular building with a flat roof, where two air conditioning units are visible on the top right corner. The main structure is connected to a covered walkway that extends horizontally along the upper portion of the image, supported by columns. To the left of the walkway, there is a parking area with a few cars and a small water feature or fountain. Below the central building, a paved plaza with geometric patterns and evenly spaced shrubs runs parallel to the structure, bordered by additional greenery and low walls. On the right side, a large open area with trees and paths suggests a park or landscaped zone, adding a natural contrast to the surrounding concrete. The image appears to be taken on a clear day, as shadows are sharp and the overall color tone is neutral, with no signs of rain or fog. The scene has a clean, organized look, but lacks human presence, giving it a calm, almost quiet atmosphere.

satellite/000020/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban building complex with a flat roof and structured layout. The central object is a large rectangular structure with a white railing around its upper level, possibly a rooftop terrace, featuring a dark, irregularly shaped area that might be a pool or garden. To the left and right of the central section, there are smaller sections with rectangular openings and staircases leading down. The building appears symmetrical and is surrounded by paved areas and pathways. The image is taken during overcast weather, with muted lighting and no visible shadows, giving the scene a neutral and slightly barren look. The surroundings seem quiet and unoccupied, with no signs of activity. The overall atmosphere is calm but lacks vibrancy due to the gray tones and lack of natural light.

satellite/000020/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with a large open courtyard. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof that has a white railing around a raised platform, which appears to be a rooftop terrace or observation deck. On the right side of the building, there are two visible air conditioning units stacked on top of each other, suggesting it is an active facility, possibly a hospital, office, or educational institution. The building has multiple large openings that resemble archways or windows on the lower level, some of which have dark openings giving a sense of depth. To the left, partially visible, is a larger structure with a curved shape. A lower, rectangular section with a yellow marked fence runs along the right side. The ground surrounding the buildings is paved with visible patterns and includes patches of greenery, possibly small trees or shrubs, placed around the courtyard. There is a pathway leading into the complex from the bottom of the frame. The sky is clear, and the sunlight is bright, casting sharp shadows on the ground, indicating it is a sunny day. The overall scene shows a clean, structured design, with a calm and organized atmosphere.

satellite/000020/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex. The central object is a large structure with a flat roof and multiple levels, featuring a prominent rooftop area with what appears to be a rooftop garden, a solar panel array, and ventilation units. There are covered walkways connecting different parts of the building. To the left of the main building, there is a long, linear area with what looks like parking spaces and a covered ramp or entryway. On the right side, the structure continues with more rooms and outdoor spaces, including staircases and open-air sections. In front of the main building, there is an organized open plaza with symmetrical patterns on the ground, benches, and several trees. The surrounding area appears urban and developed, with roads and possibly other buildings nearby. The image is taken during the day under overcast conditions, so the lighting is flat and even. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with a clean, structured design reflecting modern city planning. The colors are muted, with shades of gray and green dominating. The image gives a sense of quiet functionality and intentional layout.

satellite/000021/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban structure, likely a building complex with rooftop features. The central object is a large, flat-roofed structure with several sections and edges, featuring a series of small rectangular openings. A raised platform with a white railing extends along the top, and a dark, elongated object—possibly a vehicle or machinery—rests on one side. To the left, a taller section with horizontal lines suggests a facade or wall. The surrounding area consists of paved surfaces and dark patches that may be landscaping or shadows. The lighting is flat and even, indicating overcast conditions with no strong shadows, giving the scene a neutral, slightly muted tone. The overall atmosphere is calm and uneventful, with no visible movement or activity.

satellite/000021/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural complex with multiple levels and structured walkways. At the center of the image is a large, rectangular platform elevated above the ground, featuring a flat roof and surrounded by a metal railing. A dark shape, possibly a vehicle or piece of equipment, is visible on this rooftop. To the left of the central structure, there is a lower section with a solid, dark roof and narrow vertical panels. Below, the ground level shows a pattern of paved surfaces and several small green areas shaped like half-circles. The lower part of the image reveals a covered area with curved edges, likely a parking or transit space. The scene is captured under uniform, flat lighting, suggesting an overcast day with no shadows. The image has a calm and orderly appearance, with a balance between solid structures and open spaces. The use of muted gray and white tones gives it a clean, industrial look.

satellite/000021/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban building complex, likely a school or institutional facility, captured from a high angle. The main structure is a multi-level building with a flat roof and a large open courtyard in the center. The courtyard contains a few small green areas and a walkway with a railing along the top level. The building has a modern, geometric design with rectangular shapes and sharp angles. On the right side of the image, there are two air conditioning units mounted on the roof, indicating the building's functional layout. To the left, a darker section of the complex appears to be a covered area or a different stage of the building, possibly a parking garage or storage space. The surrounding area is paved with a patterned surface, and there are some trees visible at the edge of the frame, adding a touch of nature to the otherwise structured environment. The scene is bathed in soft daylight, suggesting a clear day with no visible clouds, creating a bright and orderly atmosphere. Overall, the image conveys a sense of calm and organization, typical of a well-maintained urban space.

satellite/000022/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with flat rooftops and balconies. On the left, a dark rectangular structure with a glass railing stands above a lighter section of the roof. To the right, a lower beige building has a wide terrace enclosed by a white railing, where a black vehicle is parked. A small staircase connects nearby roof levels. Below, a dark area with circular patterns suggests a parking lot or plaza. The scene is gray and still under flat, overcast lighting, giving it a quiet, neutral atmosphere. No people are visible, and the weather appears cloudy with no signs of sunlight or rain. The overall impression is calm and uneventful, like a quiet moment in an urban setting.

satellite/000022/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with a rooftop structure. The central object is a rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring a large dark section that appears to be a solar panel array or a roof terrace. Below this, the building has a lighter, possibly concrete or stone facade with a series of rectangular windows or openings arranged in a grid pattern. To the right of the main structure, a raised level extends outward with a white railing, and a large dark shape, possibly a piece of equipment or a structure like a boat, is visible on the surface. This area has a patterned and somewhat mechanical appearance. On the left, there is a smaller, lower section of the building with a similar flat roof and a dark, flat surface. The surrounding area includes more flat surfaces, pathways, and shapes suggesting outdoor structures or landscaping, with the ground appearing dark and texturally varied. The image has a monochromatic, high-contrast look, likely due to the way the satellite or drone camera captured the light. The weather appears overcast or the image was taken during a time with limited natural light, giving the entire scene a smooth, muted appearance. The overall impression is one of functional design and geometric order, with few signs of human presence or activity.

satellite/000022/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with surrounding paved areas. The central structure features a large, flat roof with several sections and a rectangular design, shaped like a series of connected blocks. A long, narrow walkway connects parts of the building, and a small enclosed section on the right appears to house a vehicle. The roof has small raised sections, possibly solar panels or ventilation structures. To the left of the building, a street runs vertically, with a light-colored lane marked with a crosswalk at its upper end. Adjacent to the building on the lower side is a patterned courtyard with geometric designs, flanked by trees or shrubs. On the right, there is a rectangular open design with a lawn and a curved border. The surrounding area appears mostly paved, with roads and walkways forming a grid-like layout. The image is taken during the day under clear, bright conditions, as evidenced by the sharp shadows and high contrast. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, resembling a functional urban space. The grey tones of the structures and pavement contribute to a neutral, utilitarian feel.

satellite/000023/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with flat roofs and geometric design. The central structure has large dark panels on its roof and a lower section with a lighter roof, surrounded by walkways and open spaces. To the left, a paved road runs parallel to the building, with a single vehicle visible. On the right, a taller section with a balcony rises above the main structure. A row of trees lines the area in front, casting faint shadows. The scene is captured under bright daylight with clear visibility, showing sharp contrasts in light and shadow. The overall impression is one of clean, ordered architecture in an urban or institutional setting.

satellite/000023/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area captured from above. In the center of the image, there is a large building with a flat roof and a rectangular shape, featuring a section that appears to be a green or covered rooftop space. This main structure is surrounded by smaller buildings, including one with a sloped roof on the upper left and another with a white railing on the upper right. To the left of the central building, a narrow street runs vertically, with a white car visible on it, suggesting a quiet urban or suburban environment. On the lower part of the image, a long, patterned walkway or paved area stretches horizontally, lined with evenly spaced trees that create a neat, organized appearance. The scene is captured under overcast lighting conditions, with no strong shadows, giving the image a muted and neutral tone. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with minimal signs of movement or activity.

satellite/000023/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, viewed from above on a clear day. At the center of the image is a large, multi-level building with a flat roof, surrounded by paved surfaces and landscaping. The structure features a mix of dark and light-colored sections, with a prominent upper level that appears to be a rooftop terrace or mechanical area. To the left of the building, there is a street with a pedestrian crossing and a sidewalk running parallel. A row of parked vehicles lines the street, and a few trees are visible along the edge of the pavement. On the right side, a smaller structure with balcony railings extends outward, possibly a residential or observatory section. The surrounding area includes concrete pathways, low walls, and a small triangular green space with trees. The image has a clean, organized layout, with symmetry in the roads and buildings. The weather is bright and clear, with no clouds or shadows, giving the scene a calm and order-filled appearance.

satellite/000024/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex in an urban area. The central object is a rectangular structure with a flat, dark roof and large windows arranged in a grid pattern. To the left, there is a curved section with a pointed edge, possibly part of a parking garage or entrance. A paved area with parked vehicles is next to the building, showing faint tire marks and a few trees. Nearby, a small green space with overgrown bushes is visible. The surrounding structures are mostly low-rise, with a mix of flat and semi-enclosed spaces. The image is slightly blurry, suggesting it might have been taken on a cloudy day with diffused lighting. The overall scene feels calm and quiet, with no visible people or traffic.

satellite/000024/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, likely a section of a business or institutional complex. In the center of the image stands a large rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring multiple rows of dark solar panels, indicating a focus on energy efficiency. The building has a gray facade and appears to be well-maintained, with clean lines and organized structure. To the left, a smaller building with a curved roof is visible, possibly a pavilion or parking structure, surrounded by paved walkways and small patches of greenery. A narrow road runs vertically through the image, separating the two main buildings and showing minimal traffic. To the right of the main building, additional structures are partially visible, suggesting a larger campus or development. The sunlight is bright and direct, casting short, sharp shadows, indicating a clear day with no clouds. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with a sense of function and design.

satellite/000024/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, captured from above on a clear day with bright sunlight. At the center of the image stands a large, rectangular building with a flat roof and dark windows, appearing solid and functional. To the left, a series of lower structures form a uniform block, with paved spaces and parking areas between them. A narrow road with a pedestrian crossing runs vertically along the center, dividing the scene and guiding the eye through it. On the right side, another building with a similar architectural style extends from the main structure, showing a clean, geometric design. Sparse trees and light-colored walkways surround the buildings, giving the area a structured and orderly look. The shadows cast by the buildings are sharp and long, indicating either early morning or late afternoon. There is no sign of people or vehicles, which adds to the quiet and still atmosphere of the scene. The overall impression is of a clean, well-maintained city space, possibly part of a business or campus district. The lighting is consistent and natural, suggesting good weather without clouds or haze.

satellite/000025/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with buildings and paved spaces. In the center, there is a large, open paved square with a grid-like pattern and a curved building near the top. To the left, a low structure with a flat roof is visible, and to the right, a taller building with a rectangular shape and several protruding sections stands. A narrow street runs vertically along the right edge, with a small white car passing by. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with no people or heavy activity. The image was taken in daylight under fair conditions, with clear visibility and no signs of rain or fog. The buildings are mostly dark gray, contrasting with the lighter pavement, creating a functional and unremarkable cityscape at rest.

satellite/000025/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area, likely taken during early morning or late afternoon, as the lighting appears soft and diffused with long shadows stretching across the scene. In the center, a narrow street runs vertically, flanked by buildings on both sides. On the left, there is a multi-story structure with a flat roof and a curved section on the upper level, partially covered in what looks like metal or concrete panels. At the bottom left, a low-rise building with a simple rectangular form stands beside some greenery. To the right, a more modern structure with a flat roof and large horizontal windows dominates the view. Below it, a paved area with a grid-like pattern is visible, possibly a parking lot or plaza. A white vehicle is seen on the street, moving toward the top of the image. The surroundings include scattered trees and patches of dark, shadowed ground, giving the area a quiet, still feel. The image lacks bright colors, with muted tones of gray, brown, and green dominating the scene, creating a calm and somewhat subdued atmosphere. There is no sign of rain or fog, but the lighting suggests an overcast or slightly hazy day.

satellite/000025/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with buildings and streets. On the left side, there is a long rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring a curved section at one end. In the center, a paved courtyard with a grid pattern is visible, bordered by a narrow road. To the right, a modern building with a dark roof and large windows stands adjacent to the courtyard. The streets form a simple layout with a crosswalk visible at the top center. A single vehicle can be seen on the road, suggesting light traffic. The image is taken during the day with clear visibility, and the sky appears bright, indicating fair weather. The overall scene has a quiet and orderly atmosphere, typical of a city district with organized architecture and minimal activity.

satellite/000026/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex. The central object is a large structure with a flat roof and a curved extension on the right, connected by a covered walkway. A grid-like paved courtyard lies in front, surrounded by landscaped green areas with small trees. To the left, a lower concrete building sits beside a narrow pathway. On the right, a road runs parallel to the site, with a faintly visible car on the pavement. The image appears to have been taken on a clear day under bright sunlight, casting subtle shadows that emphasize the building’s geometric lines. The overall scene is calm, with a clean, orderly design and a sense of quiet functionality.

satellite/000026/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet neighborhood with several buildings and a paved area. In the center, there is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof and a small curved section on one end, possibly a school or community center. To the left, a long building stretches along the edge, with a smaller structure in front, possibly a garage or shed. On the right, a partially visible house stands beside a wide road, with trees lining the sidewalk. The road runs vertically through the frame, separating the buildings on the left from the one on the right. A few trees and patches of grass appear around the structures, giving the area a slight green touch. The pavement consists of square tiles, creating a neat pattern. The scene is calm and orderly, with no people or vehicles visible. The lighting suggests it was taken during the day under cloudy or overcast skies, giving the image a slightly flat and muted tone. There is no sign of rain or fog. Overall, the image feels peaceful and still, capturing a quiet moment in an urban area.

satellite/000026/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with several buildings and paved spaces. In the center, there is a large building with a flat roof and a curved section on the right side, connected by a walkway. To the left of this structure, a series of rectangular buildings lie in a linear arrangement, each with a flat roof and visible windows. The ground space between and around the buildings includes paved walkways and sections of greenery, such as trees and shrubs. On the right side of the image, a smaller building with a dark roof stands near the edge, adjacent to a road that runs vertically upward. Scattered along the road are white lines marking lanes and crosswalks. The image has a grayish tone, suggesting overcast or cloudy weather, with no visible shadows or bright sunlight. The atmosphere is calm and still, without signs of people or vehicles, giving the area a peaceful and unused appearance. The overall scene feels isolated and quiet, with a sense of order in the layout of the structures and streets.

satellite/000027/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex with multiple interconnected structures. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, surrounded by smaller sections and walkways. On the left, a curved wing extends from the main structure, while on the right, a series of steps and a paved courtyard lead to a curved ramp or entrance. A small green area is visible between the buildings, possibly a garden or courtyard. The surface of the complex appears dark and weathered, suggesting age or exposure. The image is taken from above, providing a top-down view that emphasizes the geometric layout of the architecture. There is no visible activity, giving the scene a quiet and still atmosphere. The weather is clear, with no clouds or rain, allowing for a sharp and detailed view of the structures.

satellite/000027/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex surrounded by a paved courtyard and some greenery. The central structure consists of several rectangular sections connected by walkways, forming a U-shaped layout with a courtyard in the middle. The rooftop is flat with some visible equipment and structures, possibly ventilation units or air conditioning systems. To the left of the building, there is a curved section with steps leading down, suggesting a ramp or access point. On the right side, there is a grid-like pavement pattern, likely a parking area or plaza, with one visible white line marking a boundary. Trees and shrubs are scattered around the edges, adding green patches to the otherwise gray and beige urban scene. The image appears to be taken on an overcast day, with soft lighting and no strong shadows, giving the area a calm and slightly subdued atmosphere. The overall impression is one of quiet functionality, typical of a government or institutional facility.

satellite/000027/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex with a geometric design, captured during daylight under overcast skies. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, featuring a prominent curved section on the right side and a smaller, angular extension on the left. The central area includes a paved courtyard surrounded by walkways and small green patches. To the right of the main building, a straight road runs vertically, with a few visible vehicles and a crosswalk at the top edge. On the lower left, a series of connected low-rise buildings create a smaller architectural block. The surrounding area consists of dark green trees and shrubs, suggesting a controlled, structured landscape. The overall impression is one of order and functionality, with no human presence visible. The light is flat and diffused due to cloud cover, giving the scene a neutral, cool tone. The image is precise, with clear contrasts between the gray concrete surfaces and the darker surrounding vegetation. This quiet, structured environment conveys a sense of modern urban planning, possibly a school, government facility, or cultural center, captured in a calm and unassuming moment.

satellite/000028/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure, possibly a parking garage or a multi-level building complex. The central object is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, surrounded by elevated walkways and ramps. On the left, a section of the structure extends diagonally, forming a stair-like incline. Below the central building, a dark, open space suggests a courtyard or an enclosed area. The surrounding concrete surfaces are smooth and gray, with some parts showing signs of wear. There are no visible people or vehicles, giving the scene a still and quiet feeling. Shadows are soft, indicating indirect sunlight, possibly during early morning or late afternoon. The overall atmosphere is calm and unpopulated, with the stark geometry of the concrete creating a sense of order and rigidity. The weather appears clear, with no signs of rain or fog.

satellite/000028/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large structure surrounded by greenery. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, connected to other smaller sections by covered walkways, forming a cross-like shape. To the left, a lower building with a similar roof design stands adjacent, while on the right, more low-rise structures are visible, some open to the air. The surrounding area is covered with trees, and a patch of what appears to be a dark pond or wet area lies between the buildings. There are no visible people or vehicles, and the scene is captured in daylight under clear conditions. The colors are muted—grays of the concrete and dark greens of the foliage—giving the image a calm and orderly feel. The lack of movement and activity creates a sense of stillness, as if the space is temporarily at rest. The overall atmosphere is quiet and structured, with the design of the buildings suggesting a functional purpose, such as a community center or institutional complex.
