satellite/000054/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city square with a modern architectural structure. In the center, a circular plaza with a patterned design and some greenery is visible, surrounded by wide pathways. To the upper part of the image, there is a large building complex with flat roofs and rectangular openings, possibly entrances or windows. On the left side, a series of smaller buildings and trees form a green border. On the right, a less developed area with some visible fencing and unused land is present. The overall scene appears to be in daylight with clear visibility, suggesting fair weather. The image is in grayscale, which gives the area a neutral and slightly stark atmosphere. The layout shows symmetry and order, with open spaces allowing for movement and activity. The architecture is utilitarian, and the area seems to be designed for public use. There are no people or vehicles visible, which contributes to a sense of quiet and stillness. The design elements include geometric shapes and clean lines, indicating a planned and structured environment. This mostly empty space suggests it may not be a peak time for visitors.

satellite/000054/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban landscape featuring a large, circular plaza at the center. The plaza has a symmetrical design with concentric rings leading to a central feature that appears to be a fountain or monument. Surrounding the circle are paved walkways and flower beds arranged in geometric shapes. To the left and right of the plaza, rectangular buildings with flat roofs stand in a structured layout, and a bridge or walkway connects structures in the background. A wide avenue with vehicle markings runs horizontally across the upper section of the image, separating the plaza from the buildings in the distance. The overall composition has a formal, planned look with clean lines and balanced design, suggesting a city square or public space. The image is in grayscale, giving it a calm and unemotional tone, possibly due to overcast weather. The lighting is flat and even, with no shadows, indicating a cloudy day or a filtered satellite view. There are no people or moving vehicles visible, giving the scene a quiet, still atmosphere.

satellite/000055/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a symmetrical urban plaza with a central circular design. The center features a round area with radiating paths and what appears to be a fountain or monument at the middle. Surrounding this are evenly spaced curved sections with dark shapes, likely benches or planters. Moving outward, the plaza has a checkerboard pattern of light and dark tiles, forming a grid. On both sides of the upper part, there are rectangular structures, possibly water features or buildings, with curved landscaping. To the left and right, darker shapes suggest trees or shaded walkways. The overall layout is orderly and balanced. The lighting is flat and uniform, indicating an overcast day with no visible shadows, contributing to a calm and still atmosphere.

satellite/000055/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza with symmetrical design features. At the center is a large circular area with a radial pattern of walkways and dark, rounded planters or seating spaces, creating a strong geometric focus. Surrounding this is a wide, paved open space with light-colored stone or concrete tiles, forming a grid-like pattern. Around the edges of the plaza, there are rectangular buildings with flat roofs and some shaded areas, possibly due to overhangs or nearby structures. On the left side, a curved section of wall or low structure appears, while the right side shows more open space with faint lines that may be pathways or markings. The image is in black and white, suggesting it was taken on a clear day with bright, even lighting and no visible shadows or clouds. The overall impression is one of order and simplicity, with a sense of calm in the structured layout of the space.

satellite/000055/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large outdoor plaza with a central circular design. The center features a round structure with a fountain or monument at its core, surrounded by ascending steps and seating areas in the shape of a semi-circle. The plaza is paved with light-colored tiles, forming a grid-like pattern. To the left and right of the plaza, there are more open spaces with pathways, some green areas with bushes, and at the far end, a building with a flat roof and a railing above a lower-level entryway. The space appears empty and quiet, with no people visible. The lighting suggests a clear day with strong sunlight, creating sharp shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, showing a carefully planned urban environment. The layout mixes open areas with structured elements, showing a balance between function and design. The scene is peaceful, with no signs of motion or activity in the moment captured.

satellite/000056/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a paved urban area, showing a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, a large circular structure, possibly a fountain or plaza, has a patterned design with curved sections extending outward. To the left, a rectangular building with a flat roof stands with dark windows, while to the right, another building with vertical windows is visible. A wide, straight path runs through the middle, lined with what appear to be trees or small buildings. The entire scene is captured under neutral lighting, making the details clear and straightforward. The image has a quiet, structured feel, lacking any signs of people or movement, giving it a still and organized atmosphere. There is no indication of rain or clouds; the weather appears clear and calm.

satellite/000056/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza surrounded by buildings. At the center, a circular design features concentric rings and seating areas, creating a focal point for gathering. The plaza is paved with light-colored tiles arranged in a geometric pattern, forming rectangular sections with darker borders. To the left, a series of rounded, tiered terraces descend in levels, possibly serving as steps or ledges. The right side of the image shows the lower portion of a large building with flat roofs and square windows; parts of its structure appear to be made of glass and steel. A narrow walkway lines the perimeter, bordered by small trees or shrubs in a neat row. The image appears to be taken on a clear day with mild sunlight that casts soft shadows, emphasizing the layout and form of the space. The overall scene feels orderly and structured, suggesting a planned public area designed for both function and visual balance. No people or vehicles are visible, giving it a calm and still atmosphere.

satellite/000056/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban space, likely a public square or plaza adjacent to a large building. In the center is a circular design with concentric rings and radiating elements, resembling a sunburst or a compass, with a small structure or fountain at the very middle. The area is surrounded by a patterned pavement with repeating square designs, and several curved walkways lead between sections. To the left, a raised section contains parked vehicles and some greenery, while a low wall or fence runs along the edge. The building in the upper portion has a flat roof with what appear to be solar panels or dark roofing material, and a light-colored facade with basal elements. To the right, there's a raised platform with railings, possibly a viewing area or balcony. The entire scene appears dry and well-lit under even daylight, suggesting a clear day. The colors are primarily neutral—grays, beiges, and muted greens—giving the space a calm, orderly appearance. There is no visible movement or people, contributing to a still and quiet atmosphere.

satellite/000057/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area with a prominent rectangular plaza at its center. The plaza features a patterned design with repeating square shapes and is surrounded by pathways and green spaces with trees and bushes. To the left is a street with parked cars and a few moving vehicles, while to the right is a curved walkway bordered by a low wall and some landscaping. On the top edge, there is a large building with a flat roof and visible mechanical equipment. A few people can be seen walking along the paths, adding movement to the scene. The image appears to be taken on a clear day with bright sunlight, casting short shadows and enhancing the contrast between light and dark areas. The overall atmosphere is orderly and functional, typical of a well-maintained public space in a city.

satellite/000057/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center of the image, a large rectangular paved plaza stretches horizontally, featuring a patterned design with darker tiles forming a grid. The plaza is bordered on the left by a narrow road with a single white car parked along the side. To the right, part of a curved building with a flat roof is visible, showing a modern design with clean lines. On the upper side of the image, a larger structure with a dark roof and some green areas on its top surface stands prominently. A row of evenly spaced trees lines the edge of the plaza, providing shade and a touch of nature. In the lower section, a curved walkway leads toward a round, open space with seating areas, suggesting a public gathering spot. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no people visible. The lighting suggests a clear day with mild shadows, indicating it is either morning or afternoon. There is no sign of fog or rain, and the scene appears well-maintained and peaceful.

satellite/000057/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a mix of architectural and landscape elements. In the center of the image is a large open plaza with a rectangular pattern of light-colored paving stones, bordered by rows of small trees that create a calm, orderly appearance. To the left, a wide street runs vertically, with a few parked cars visible along the side. A large building with a flat roof and a section of dark solar panels dominates the upper part of the frame, its clean lines suggesting a commercial or institutional use. On the right, a curved structure with tiered, circular patterns and dark shaded areas appears to be a decorative or functional feature, such as a fountain or plaza, adding visual interest to the space. Surrounding the plaza are patches of greenery, including trees and shrubs that soften the hard geometry of the built environment. The lighting is even and bright, indicating a clear day with no visible clouds, and the overall image conveys a sense of quiet order and structured urban design. The gray tones and sharp details give it a clean and modern look.

satellite/000058/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a large rectangular area covered with a grid of square patterns, possibly a plaza or courtyard, with some trees arranged along its edge. To the left, a paved surface with a pattern of squares features a small patch of greenery, while a narrow road runs alongside it. On the right, a curved structure, perhaps a walkway or ramp, borders a low building with flat roofing. The upper portion shows a larger building with a flat roof, and there are faint signs of activity, such as a small vehicle near the bottom center. The lighting is neutral, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows, giving the scene a flat, muted tone. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with clean lines and a sense of geometric precision.

satellite/000058/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, likely a campus or institutional complex, captured from high above on a clear day with bright sunlight. In the center of the image, there is a large open paved area with a patterned floor, possibly a courtyard or plaza, bordered by trees and benches. To the left, a network of walkways and small green spaces forms a grid-like layout, leading to a building partially visible at the upper left corner with a flat roof and angular shape. On the right side, a prominent structure with a modern, rectangular design rises, featuring a dark facade and multiple windows, likely an administrative or educational building. A small parking area with several cars is visible below the plaza, near the bottom center. The scene feels organized and calm, with no visible people, suggesting a moment of stillness. The crisp shadows and clean lines emphasize the geometric design of the space, conveying a sense of order and quiet functionality. The overall atmosphere is peaceful, with the bright sun enhancing the sharp contrasts and textures of the buildings and pavement.

satellite/000058/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a mix of buildings, open spaces, and roads. In the center, a wide paved area with a grid of light-colored tiles stretches out, surrounded by darker pavement and a few trees. To the left, a tall building with flat surfaces stands beside a smaller structure that appears to have a parking zone on the ground, with a few cars visible. On the right side, a curved, slightly raised structure with tiered levels suggests a plaza or amphitheater, possibly used for gatherings or performances. A narrow road cuts vertically through the image, bordered by sidewalks and trees, connecting different parts of the area. The scene is captured under clear daylight with even lighting, casting soft shadows that help outline shapes and spaces. There is no visible movement, giving the scene a calm and orderly look. The buildings are mostly simple, boxy designs, and the overall layout seems planned for both function and public use. The atmosphere is quiet and structured, characteristic of a developed urban environment.

satellite/000059/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, likely a residential or mixed-use neighborhood. In the center of the image, a narrow street runs vertically, dividing the scene into two sections. On the left, there are multiple buildings with flat roofs and small courtyards, surrounded by patches of greenery. On the right, a larger structure with a grid-like facade and modern design stands out, possibly an apartment block or office building. The area appears calm and unoccupied, with no visible people or cars. The lighting is even, suggesting an overcast day with soft, diffuse sunlight. The overall atmosphere is still and orderly, with a sense of calm urban planning. The architecture is functional, and the layout feels balanced and well-structured.

satellite/000059/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, showing a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, a paved open area with a grid pattern stands out, possibly a plaza or courtyard, surrounded by trees and pathways. To the left, a low-rise structure with a flat roof appears, partially shaded by nearby trees. On the right side of the image, a larger building with a dark roof extends vertically, while near the bottom right corner, a curved path or roadway is visible, suggesting a parking lot or a small road. A white vehicle is parked near the lower center. The scene appears under overcast conditions, as there are no clear shadows, giving the image a flat and muted look. The area looks still and calm, with no visible movement or people. Overall, the atmosphere is subdued and orderly, typical of a city block in the early morning or on a cloudy day.

satellite/000059/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a paved courtyard with a grid-like pattern, surrounded by structures with flat roofs and narrow walkways. To the left, a large building with a rectangular shape and multiple levels stands beside a smaller, angular structure. On the right, a wider open area features rows of trees and what appears to be a parking lot or plaza with marked sections. A curved pathway runs along the lower right edge, bordered by greenery and a low wall. The image has a neutral tone, with muted grays and browns dominating the scene. The weather appears overcast, resulting in soft shadows and an even light across the landscape, giving the area a calm and orderly feel. There is no visible activity, which contributes to the stillness and sense of emptiness.

satellite/000060/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings and paved surfaces. On the left, a large structure with a flat roof and a long, open-sided section stands prominently. To the right, a paved road runs vertically, with smaller buildings and parked cars visible. Trees and greenery are scattered around the scene, providing contrast to the concrete and asphalt. The image has a dull and gray tone, with no indication of sunlight or bright weather. Overall, the scene feels quiet and still, with a sense of quiet order in the layout of the space. The muted colors and lack of movement give it a calm and somewhat distant atmosphere.

satellite/000060/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, likely a residential or mixed-use neighborhood. In the center, a paved courtyard with a grid-like pattern stands between several buildings, surrounded by low structures with flat roofs. To the left, a larger building with a long rectangular shape and a series of small ridged sections on its roof dominates the view. The surrounding area includes patches of dark green vegetation and dirt areas, suggesting some undeveloped land. To the right, a narrow street runs vertically, bordered by what appears to be a parked vehicle and a fenced lot with equal-sized plots, possibly for storage or small gardens. The image has a neutral, soft light suggesting daytime with overcast skies, giving the scene a calm and uneventful atmosphere. There is no visible movement or activity. The overall tone feels subdued and still, with muted colors and no bright contrasts. The view is clear and detailed, likely captured from a satellite or drone, showing the layout of the area in a straightforward, factual manner.

satellite/000060/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing buildings and roads from above. In the center of the image, there is a large paved area with a grid-like pattern, possibly a parking lot or open space, surrounded by concrete walls and pathways. To the left, a long rectangular building with a flat roof runs horizontally, connected to other structures. On the right, a paved area with small dark patches suggests parked vehicles or shaded spots. A narrow road cuts vertically through the center, connecting the different sections. The surrounding greenery is scattered, mainly in tree clusters and small patches of grass. The image does not show people or moving vehicles, giving the scene a still and calm feel. The lighting suggests an overcast day, with no clear shadows or bright sunlight. The overall atmosphere is quiet and orderly, typical of an urban environment viewed from a distance.

satellite/000061/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city with buildings and paved areas. In the center, there is a long, narrow building with a flat roof and several windows, possibly a small industrial or utility structure. To the left of this building, a larger rectangular structure is visible, with a plain facade and a noticeable corner piece. On the right, a grid-like pattern of tiles covers a flat surface that could be a parking lot or open plaza. Surrounding these structures are dark patches of ground covered with trees or bushes, giving the scene a mixed appearance of built environments and nature. The lighting appears to be natural, suggesting daytime, though the image has a slightly muted tone, possibly due to overcast weather. The overall look is functional and urban, with little decoration or softness.

satellite/000061/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a collection of buildings and open spaces, likely a campus or institutional area. In the center, there is a long, rectangular structure with a flat roof, possibly a gymnasium or a classroom building, with a covered walkway extending from its side. To the left, a lighter-colored building with a similar flat roof is visible, connected to the central structure by a low wall. On the right, a paved courtyard with a grid-like pattern of tiles and a few green shrubs appears, bordered by a path that leads to a darker area, possibly a parking lot. The surrounding ground is a mix of earthy tones and patches of greenery, suggesting sparse vegetation and some natural terrain in between the built structures. The image is taken under overcast or cloudy conditions, as the lighting is soft and uniform, with no strong shadows. The atmosphere is neutral and functional, with no signs of movement or human activity. The overall scene feels ordered and quiet, with a sense of distance and stillness.

satellite/000061/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings and open spaces. In the center of the image, there is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof, possibly a warehouse or an industrial building. To the left of this building are other structures with similar flat rooftops and grey walls, surrounded by paved ground and patches of green vegetation. On the right side, there is a paved area with lighter square patterns, likely a parking lot or courtyard, and a narrow road runs alongside it with a few vehicles visible near the edge. A small, dark patch of trees appears beneath the central building, indicating a garden or landscaping area. The overall scene looks orderly and calm, with no visible movement. The image has a cool, neutral tone, suggesting it was taken on an overcast day or during a time when sunlight was dim. No rain or fog is apparent, just a quiet urban landscape captured from above.

satellite/000062/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern concrete structure, possibly a building or a series of platforms. The center of the image shows a flat, rectangular construction with a smooth surface and a light gray color, surrounded by darker sections that indicate shadows or lower levels. To the left, there is another section of the structure with similar material, and on the right, a vertical wall rises upward, showing the edge of the building. Below the main structure, a dark, textured area appears to be a natural terrain or ground cover, possibly vegetation. The scene is taken under overcast conditions, with no strong shadows, giving the image a muted and somber tone. The overall atmosphere is quiet and industrial, with a sense of stillness due to the lack of movement or human presence. The view is clear but lacks bright colors, creating a neutral and functional impression.

satellite/000062/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure surrounded by greenery. In the center of the image, a long rectangular building with a flat roof is visible, flanked by smaller, similarly styled buildings. To the right, a paved area with a patterned grid of tiles extends outward, likely a courtyard or walkway. On the left, there is a curved concrete structure that suggests part of a larger complex or enclosure. The surrounding area features dense vegetation, with dark patches of trees and bushes filling the space between the structures. The overall scene appears quiet and still. The lighting is neutral, suggesting an overcast day with no strong sunlight or shadows visible. The atmosphere is calm, almost muted, as if captured during a moment of quiet in an urban or institutional environment. The image has a slightly grainy texture, common in high-altitude satellite photography, lending it a detached, observational feel. There are no signs of people or movement.

satellite/000062/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, complex structure, likely a school or institutional campus. In the center is a long, low building with a flat roof, flanked by several rectangular wings extending to the sides. To the left, a series of stepped levels rise in tiers, possibly forming part of a stadium or amphitheater, with dark patches that might be trees or shadows. On the right, a paved area laid out in a grid pattern suggests an open courtyard or parking lot. The surrounding grounds show patches of greenery, including some visible trees and shrubs, contrasting with the gray concrete and stone of the buildings. A narrow path or road runs along the bottom edge. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with no people or vehicles visible. The lighting suggests an overcast day, giving the image a muted, gray tone, which adds to the quiet and structured atmosphere of the site. The image conveys a sense of stillness and precision, with the layout emphasizing function and design.

satellite/000063/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a concrete structure, likely a dam or bridge, viewed from above. The central object is a large, blocky building with flat surfaces and sharp angles, built from gray concrete. To the left, a section extends further with what appears to be a walkway or bridge. On the right, there are lower-level sections with curved architectural shapes, possibly arches or support structures. The area beneath the main structure is dark, suggesting water or shadowed terrain. The overall scene is muted, with gray and dark tones dominating the view. The image is taken under overcast skies, contributing to the flat, lifeless lighting and a quiet, industrial atmosphere. There is no sign of people or movement, giving the place a still and unoccupied feeling.

satellite/000063/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a complex urban area with several large buildings. In the center of the image, there is a long rectangular structure with a flat roof, which appears to be a stadium or large hall. To the left of this central building, there are smaller structures with dark, flat rooftops, including a short block with a light-colored facade. On the right side, a series of long, narrow buildings run parallel to each other, forming a low-rise row with multiple angular roofs. Some parts of the surrounding area are covered in dense greenery, suggesting landscaped grounds or trees. The image is taken from a high angle, capturing the geometric shapes and layout of the developed space. The lighting is neutral, with no strong shadows, indicating an overcast day. The overall atmosphere is quiet and functional, lacking the vibrancy seen in more active urban environments. The textures are mostly gray and brown, with muted tones that give the scene a calm and orderly feel. There are no people or moving vehicles visible, adding to the stillness of the image.

satellite/000063/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a complex of large concrete structures, likely part of an urban or industrial development. In the center, a long rectangular building runs horizontally, surrounded by other buildings of similar size and shape, creating a grid-like layout. To the upper left, a taller structure stands out with stepped levels, while lower buildings sit to the lower left. On the right side, a series of flat-roofed buildings form a linear arrangement, partially shaded by nearby trees. Between the buildings, dark patches of greenery and shadows suggest landscaping or unoccupied land. The lighting is even and diffuse, indicating an overcast day with no strong sunlight or shadows. The overall scene appears quiet and empty, with no visible people or vehicles. The gray tones of the concrete dominate the image, giving it a utilitarian and somewhat stark appearance. The layout suggests functionality over aesthetics, typical of institutional or commercial zones. There is no visible movement, and the scene feels still and unchanging. The image conveys a sense of order and structure, but also a lack of vibrancy or warmth.

satellite/000064/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex, likely an institutional or governmental structure, situated in an urban area. The central object is a multi-story building with a flat roof and large rectangular sections, showing signs of age with weathered walls and dark patches. To the left, a smaller structure with a glass facade reflects light, contrasting with the matte surface of the main building. On the right, a curved, lower wall with rounded openings forms part of an older architectural element, possibly a historical addition. The surrounding area includes additional buildings and open spaces, with a dark, shadowy ground suggesting low sunlight or overcast conditions. The scene appears quiet and still, with muted colors and a sense of stillness conveyed by the lack of movement or people.

satellite/000064/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, unfinished construction site. In the center, a concrete structure with multiple levels and flat surfaces is visible, resembling a multi-story building in early stages of development. Surrounding this main object are various other structures and ground areas, some with flat rooftops and others with a more irregular appearance. To the left, there is a smaller adjacent section with visible walls and open spaces. On the right side, parts of the site appear more densely built, with lots of concrete and metallic surfaces. The scene appears to be under a strong, clear sky with bright daylight, casting sharp shadows across the structures. There are no visible people or vehicles, giving the area a quiet and still feel. The dominant color is gray, from the concrete and steel, creating a stark and industrial atmosphere. There are no signs of vegetation or natural elements, emphasizing the artificial nature of the environment. The overall mood is one of stillness and unfinished purpose, suggesting a place in transition.

satellite/000064/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex with multiple connected structures and flat roofs, viewed from above. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a smooth gray roof and a series of smaller platforms and extensions along its sides. To the left of this central building, a curved, dark surface — likely a parking area or a large patio — is visible, bordered by darker green patches that suggest trees or landscaping. On the right, other buildings with similar flat, gray rooftops extend outward, forming a sprawling urban layout. In the lower part of the image, a series of clearly marked rectangles — probably parking spaces — form a grid close to a lower-level section of the complex. The ground appears mostly paved, with only small areas showing vegetation. The lighting is even and diffuse, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows. There is no visible activity, and the scene has a quiet, static feel. Overall, the image conveys a sense of order and function, typical of a modern institutional or commercial site.

satellite/000065/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex, likely a shopping mall or public facility, surrounded by paved areas and some greenery. The main structure has a flat, elongated roof with distinct sections, including a central part that appears to be a covered walkway or entrance. To the left, there is a curved section with a glass facade and a parking area below, while the right side contains more open and flat roof spaces. Smaller buildings and parking lots are situated around the main structure. The ground is mostly paved, with faint lanes and some shade from trees. The image was taken on a clear day with bright sunlight, casting deep shadows and highlighting the smooth, gray surfaces. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, lacking any signs of activity or people.

satellite/000065/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a large, modern building complex. In the center of the frame, a multi-story building with a flat roof and rectangular shape stands out, surrounded by paved walkways and small green spaces. To the left, a curved section of the building is visible, possibly a lower wing or entrance, with a covered area above it. A wide street with clear lane markings intersects the scene on the lower left, while faint road lines run between the buildings. The overall lighting suggests a day with overcast skies, casting soft shadows and giving the image a grayish tone. The architecture appears functional and minimal, with no decorative details. There are no vehicles or people visible, adding a sense of stillness and emptiness to the scene. Around the buildings, patches of trees and shrubs provide small areas of green, contrasting with the dominant concrete and asphalt. The image captures a quiet and organized part of a city, with a focus on structure and layout rather than activity.

satellite/000065/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with a mix of buildings and roads. In the center, there is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof, likely a public or commercial building, surrounded by paved areas and some greenery. To the left, a curved road with white lane markings runs alongside a smaller parking area with a few cars. There is also a roundabout near the bottom left corner. To the right, another building with visible balconies and window lines stands close to the central structure. Near the top, a small parking lot with mostly empty spaces is visible. The overall area appears calm and orderly, with a clean layout of streets and driveways. The image shows a typical urban planning scene, with structures and roads occupying the space neatly. The lighting is even, suggesting it was taken during the day under light cloud cover. The atmosphere is neutral, resembling a quiet section of a city without visible movement or activity.

satellite/000066/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with a large building complex. On the left, a road curves around and connects to a crosswalk, with a roundabout visible below. The central part of the image shows a large structure with a light-colored roof and a curved section, likely a parking garage or covered walkway. To the right, a taller building with multiple floors and rectangular windows rises beside the main structure. The area is surrounded by trees and paved surfaces, with clear lines marking lanes and paths. The scene is captured under bright, even daylight, with no visible clouds or shadows, giving it a neutral and functional appearance. There is no movement or signs of activity, making the scene appear calm and orderly.

satellite/000066/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a mix of roads, buildings, and green spaces. In the center of the image, there is a large, dark, curved shape that looks like a sunken garden or a courtyard, surrounded by paved walkways and light-colored structures. To the left, a road runs diagonally with a crosswalk and a roundabout, where a few vehicles are visible, suggesting a modest flow of traffic. On the right and bottom, there are several rectangular buildings with flat roofs, likely residential or commercial, arranged in a dense layout. Trees and shrubs are scattered around the area, adding a touch of green to the concrete environment. The sky appears overcast, giving the image a flat, grayish tone with no shadows or bright sunlight. The overall atmosphere is calm and impersonal, typical of a city block observed from above, with no signs of people or active movement.

satellite/000066/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing streets, buildings, and a roundabout. In the center of the image, a roundabout with a white crosswalk pattern is visible, surrounded by paved roads. To the right, there is a large, multi-level building with flat surfaces and open spaces, possibly a parking structure or part of a complex. Near the top, several paved areas with rows of parking spots and a few vehicles can be seen. On the left, a road runs diagonally into the frame, with several parked cars along the side, indicating a less busy part of the city. The overall view is clear and lacks significant shadows, suggesting it was taken during the day under bright, even lighting. The scene appears calm and structured, with no visible movement or activity, giving it a quiet and orderly atmosphere. The surroundings include trees and small green spaces, providing a contrast to the concrete and asphalt. There are no signs of rain or fog; the sky appears clear. The overall color tone is muted, with gray tones dominating the landscape, which reflects the typical urban palette.

satellite/000067/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection with a roundabout at its center. The roundabout is surrounded by paved roads, one of which has a clearly marked crosswalk. On the left side of the image, there are small green patches of trees and a few parked cars along the street. A curved road runs along the top edge, bordered by trees and leading toward the roundabout. On the right, a large curved structure, possibly a building roof or a pedestrian overpass, stands out in the composition. The buildings appear low and blocky, with a grid-like pattern visible in the lower right section. The scene looks slightly dark and misty, suggesting a cloudy or overcast day. The overall impression is of a quiet, orderly area with minimal activity.

satellite/000067/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with a roundabout at the center. The roundabout is surrounded by paved paths and roads that curve around it, forming a symmetrical layout. To the left, a crosswalk and a street with cars leading into the roundabout are visible, while to the right, there is a large rectangular area with shade trees and what appears to be a parking space for a few vehicles. A series of buildings with flat roofs dominate the right side of the image, featuring clean lines and grey tones. In the upper section, a more open area with additional greenery and a smaller path can be seen. The overall scene appears orderly and structured, showing a typical urban environment. There is no indication of rain, fog, or bright sunlight, suggesting an overcast or neutral sky. The image has a calm and functional atmosphere, portraying a quiet moment in a developed area. The layout seems efficient and well-planned, with minimal traffic or movement visible.

satellite/000067/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with a roundabout at its center. The roundabout is surrounded by curved roads, with a clearly marked pedestrian crossing on the left side of the image. A few cars are visible on the roads, suggesting light traffic. On the left, a large building with a glass exterior stands beside green spaces filled with trees. To the right, a series of low-rise structures with flat roofs are arranged in a block-like pattern, suggesting an urban or institutional setting. A long, enclosed structure with evenly spaced windows runs along the bottom edge, possibly a parking garage or market building. The aerial view shows a mix of paved roads, sidewalks, and landscaped areas. The image appears to have been taken during the day under clear conditions, with bright lighting and no visible clouds or shadows. The overall composition reflects a functional and organized urban layout, with a calm and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/000068/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout in an urban area. The central object is a circular road intersection with a white-painted curb and lanes leading into it from multiple directions. White crosswalks are visible at the edges of the roundabout, connecting the roads to sidewalks. To the right, there is a large building with a flat roof and visible balconies, surrounded by paved surfaces. On the left, a green area with trees and a smaller structure is visible. The roads are mostly empty, suggesting a calm moment in the city. There are no visible people, cars, or signs of rain or fog, giving the scene a quiet and still appearance. The lighting appears to be neutral, possibly late afternoon, with soft shadows.

satellite/000068/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout intersection in an urban area. At the center is a circular road with a white-painted rim, allowing vehicles to move around it. Several roads connect to the roundabout, with one going vertically from the top and two extending to the sides. Crosswalks with white stripes are visible at the entry points of the roundabout. To the right, there is a large building with a flat roof and several windows, partially covered with a grid-like pattern. A smaller structure with a curved roof is near the building. To the left, the land appears more open, with patches of trees and a smaller road branching off. The ground is mostly gray concrete, with a few darker green areas indicating vegetation. The photo appears to be taken on a clear day, with no visible clouds or rain, and the lighting is even, suggesting midday conditions. The overall scene is functional and quiet, without people or vehicles in motion. The atmosphere is still and orderly, typical of a city's traffic hub area.

satellite/000068/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout in an urban area. The roundabout is circular and paved with dark asphalt, surrounded by white crosswalks that extend from the edges of the frame. Vehicles are visible on the roads leading into and out of the roundabout, indicating light traffic. To the left, there is a modern building with glass windows and a curved facade. On the right, a group of low-rise buildings with flat roofs and balconies form a block-like structure. Some trees and green spaces are scattered in the surrounding area, offering a contrast to the concrete and asphalt. The image is taken on a clear day, with bright sunlight casting short shadows, which suggests it is around midday. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, reflecting a structured city layout. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the scene appears clean and well-maintained.

satellite/000069/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection with several buildings and roads. In the center, there is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof and a paved open area in front, possibly a courtyard or plaza. To the left, a roundabout with white lane markings and a crosswalk leads into a network of streets. A curved road runs along the top edge of the image, with vehicles visible. On the right, a long building with a flat roof and multiple windows extends horizontally. The scene is captured under overcast conditions, with muted gray tones and uniform lighting. The atmosphere is calm and structured, with minimal signs of movement. Overall, the image shows a quiet section of a city, emphasizing the planned layout of streets and buildings.

satellite/000069/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection and adjacent buildings. In the center, there is a large paved area with a grid pattern, possibly a parking lot or plaza, surrounded by several rectangular structures. To the left, a roundabout with a white circular line is visible, along with a pedestrian crosswalk leading to a road curving upward. A curved overpass or elevated roadway appears in the upper left, bridging over the main street. On the right side of the image, there is a long, flat-roofed building with multiple levels, likely a commercial or institutional structure. Various vehicles can be seen on the roads, indicating moderate traffic. The image is taken during daylight with clear visibility and no signs of rain or fog. The scene has a neutral tone, with flat, dark surfaces and shadows suggesting midday sunlight. The overall mood is functional and orderly, showing a typical city environment with clean infrastructure and structured layout. The presence of paved roads, fixed crosswalks, and organized buildings conveys a sense of routine and planning.

satellite/000069/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a roundabout and surrounding buildings. In the center of the image, a roundabout with a circular island is visible, surrounded by paved roads and pedestrian crosswalks. On the left side, roads extend out from the roundabout, with a few cars on the surface, indicating a modest level of traffic. To the right, several large buildings with flat roofs are seen, including one with a multi-level structure and an adjacent open-air section. Between the roundabout and the buildings, a paved area with small patches of greenery appears, possibly a plaza or parking zone. The image has a neutral tone, likely captured on a clear day with bright sunlight, casting minimal shadows and providing clear visibility. The overall scene looks calm and orderly, typical of a city area designed for vehicle movement and public space. There is no sign of rain or fog, and the clean geometry of streets and structures gives a sense of structure and organization.

satellite/000070/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex with surrounding paved areas. The central object is a long rectangular structure with a flat roof and multiple sections, likely a public or commercial facility. To the left, a curved area with vehicles is visible, possibly a parking lot or roundabout. In front of the building, there are open spaces with geometric patterns, possibly walkways or courtyards. To the right, there is a darker, tree-lined area, possibly a park or landscaped zone. The image appears to be taken during daylight with even lighting and no visible clouds or precipitation. The overall atmosphere is calm and functional, suggesting a well-organized urban site.

satellite/000070/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban complex, likely a public or institutional building surrounded by infrastructure. The central object is a multi-winged structure with flat rooftops, possibly a school, hospital, or government building, featuring a prominent long wing extending horizontally. To the left, a curved road intersects with a street, forming a slight bend, while a smaller, round driveway or cul-de-sac curves near the corner. Rectangular paved areas resemble parking lots or courtyards, with faint grid lines indicating sidewalks or parking spaces. A few small patches of green vegetation are visible, partially hidden by shadows cast by the building. To the right, an arched, darker area may indicate a covered entrance or underpass. The entire scene appears dimly lit, suggesting either early morning or late afternoon, with long shadows and a lack of bright contrasts. There are no signs of movement or people, creating a still, quiet atmosphere typical of a low-activity time. The image has a muted, grayish tone, with no indication of rain or fog, and the overall lighting is flat and evenly diffused, giving the scene a somber and detached quality. The watermark of Google indicates the source of the satellite image.

satellite/000070/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area, showing a large building complex from above. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a flat, gray roof, which appears to be a commercial or institutional structure. To the left of this building, there is a curved road with a roundabout and a crosswalk, suggesting a busy intersection. A parking area with visible lines and a few vehicles lies in front of the building. On the right side, darker, possibly wet, surfaces suggest paved roads or plazas, and a smaller structure partially covered in vegetation can be seen behind the main building. The image has a neutral tone, with no direct sunlight or shadows, indicating overcast or cloudy weather conditions. The overall scene is quiet and organized, with no visible people or moving vehicles. The layout of streets and buildings shows a structured urban environment, giving a sense of calm order despite the complexity of the surroundings.

satellite/000071/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a complex urban area with multiple buildings and structures. In the center of the frame, there is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, connected to a lower section that appears to be an entrance or covered walkway. To the left, a modern building with a glass facade stands out against the older, more solid structures. On the right, there is a smaller structure with a sloped roof, possibly a shed or utility building. The surrounding area includes paved surfaces and a few patches of greenery, indicating a developed space. The image has a dark and muted tone, suggesting it was taken on a cloudy day with low light. The overall atmosphere is calm and quiet, with no visible people or movement, giving a sense of stillness in the urban landscape.

satellite/000071/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area showing a mix of buildings and infrastructure. In the center of the image, there is a prominent long structure with multiple sections, possibly a train station or a large warehouse, featuring flat roofs and a series of rectangular extensions. To the left of this central building, there is a lighter-colored structure with a grid-like pattern, possibly a parking lot or industrial complex. On the right, several smaller buildings are connected by a network of roads and pathways, with dense clusters of dark green areas suggesting trees or vegetation. The area appears to be in a developed city, with no visible signs of people or traffic. The lighting in the image is flat and even, with no strong shadows, indicating an overcast day. The overall tone is gray and muted, giving the scene a quiet and slightly somber feel. The image lacks high contrast and sharpness, which could be due to cloud cover or the quality of the satellite capture.

satellite/000071/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex, likely a school or institutional facility, viewed from above. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof and several attached wings. A curved section on the left suggests a separate entrance or a wing extending outward. Surrounding the main building are paved areas, including what appears to be a parking lot with marked spaces and several vehicles visible. To the right, there is a smaller, separate building with a similar flat roof. In the foreground, a series of low, rectangular structures are aligned in rows, possibly storage units or sheds. The landscape includes patches of trees and greenery, especially near the lower portion of the image. Shadows cast across the scene indicate that the sun is at a low angle, suggesting early morning or late afternoon. The image has a gray, muted tone, with no rain or fog, and the daylight is even but not bright. The overall impression is one of quiet structure and order, with a sense of stillness and routine.

satellite/000072/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with old stone structures. In the center, there is a large building with multiple arched openings, possibly an ancient bridge or tunnel entrance. To the left, a tall rectangular structure stands, and to the right, another building with flat walls and small windows is visible. The ground level appears dark, with some green patches suggesting trees or bushes. The image has a gray and muted tone, with no strong sunlight or shadows. It looks overcast, and the overall feeling is quiet and somewhat mysterious, as if capturing a forgotten part of the city. The textures are rough and weathered, giving it a historical and slightly worn appearance.

satellite/000072/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, complex building complex surrounded by greenery. The central structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof and multiple sections connected by lower structures. The main building has a light-colored facade with several rows of windows and some visible structural details like support beams. To the left, there are smaller, more modern-looking structures with glass and metal elements, while the right side features a more expansive area with what appears to be a covered section or canopy. Below the main building, there is a dark, open space that might be a parking lot or courtyard. The surrounding area includes trees and other vegetation, indicating the site is partially landscaped. The image appears to be taken during daylight, with clear visibility and minimal shadows, suggesting a cloudless day. The overall impression is of a functional, possibly institutional or educational, facility designed for large-scale use. There is no indication of people or activity, giving the scene a calm and ordered appearance.

satellite/000072/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a dense urban area with several large buildings, likely a mix of residential and institutional structures. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof and a dark facade, positioned horizontally in the center of the frame. To its left, a cluster of smaller buildings with lighter roofs and visible windows stands close together, forming a tightly packed block. On the right, another similar structure with a flat roof is partially visible, surrounded by greenery and trees that appear dark and shadowed. A wide road runs horizontally across the lower portion of the image, separating the buildings from another row below. The scene is captured under overcast conditions, with a grey sky casting even, flat light across the structures, giving the image a muted, somber tone. There is no sign of movement or activity, contributing to a still and quiet atmosphere. The architecture appears functional and modest, with little decorative detail. The overall impression is one of a typical, unremarkable section of a city where buildings stand close together, forming a continuous urban landscape.

satellite/000073/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a built-up area with several buildings and green spaces. In the center, there is a large patch of dark green vegetation, possibly a park or garden, surrounded by structures with flat or slightly sloped roofs. To the left, a long building with a vertical pattern runs along the edge, and above it, another structure with rectangular sections and a concrete facade is visible. On the right, a wider building extends horizontally, with a lighter surface that suggests a walkway or open space. The image is taken from a high angle on a cloudy day, giving the scene a muted and soft appearance. The overall lighting is even, with no strong shadows, and the colors are subdued, creating a calm and quiet urban landscape.

satellite/000073/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with several buildings and a body of water. In the center of the image is a large, dark pond or small lake, surrounded by green trees and shrubs, giving it a natural and quiet appearance. To the top of the frame are several flat-roofed structures, likely houses or apartment buildings, constructed with concrete and stone, arranged in a row. On the left side, a line of low walls and possibly a walkway follows the edge of the water, adding geometric structure to the landscape. On the right, a smaller block with lighter-colored walls and steps suggests a modern addition or entrance. The image has muted tones, with gray and green dominating the scene, and no direct sunlight is visible, indicating an overcast or cloudy day. The absence of people or movement gives the scene a still and calm feel, as if captured during a quiet moment in the early morning or late afternoon.

satellite/000073/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a building complex with a grid-like surrounding area. The central object is a large, multi-level structure with flat roofs and rectangular sections, some of which appear to have a slight overhang or balcony. The building has a modern, geometric design with clean lines and appears to be made of concrete or similar material. It is situated on the left side of the image, while the right side shows a paved surface with a regular square pattern, likely a courtyard or plaza. Between the building and the plaza, there is a narrow strip of greenery, including small trees and shrubs. The area appears to be empty of people and vehicles, giving it a calm but slightly stark appearance. The lighting suggests a cloudy or overcast day, with no strong shadows, and the overall image has a muted, grayish color tone. The atmosphere is quiet and functional, typical of an urban or institutional setting.

satellite/000074/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with several buildings and a dark green space in the center. The central part of the image shows a large patch of trees and bushes, surrounded by paved pathways and the roofs of nearby houses. To the left, a low concrete structure, possibly a deck or a covered walkway, extends over the greenery, while a tiled roof is visible on the top right, suggesting a nearby home. The image appears to be taken on an overcast day, as the lighting is flat and neutral, with no strong shadows. The overall impression is one of quiet urban life, with nature quietly blending into the built environment. The walls and paths are gray and clean, giving a sense of calm and order. The scene feels still and peaceful, like a moment of calm in a busy neighborhood.

satellite/000074/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area captured on a cloudy day, with muted lighting and a grayish tone. In the center of the image, there is a patch of dark green trees and grass, forming a small park or garden space surrounded by buildings. To the left and right, low-rise structures with flat rooftops are visible, likely apartments or homes, with some showing a light-colored surface and others appearing in shadow. A narrow road or pathway runs along the right edge of the image, with a single white vehicle parked near the sidewalk. The area appears still and quiet, with no people or movement visible, suggesting a peaceful neighborhood in the early morning or late afternoon. The lack of bright sunlight and the dense cloud cover give the scene a subdued, calm atmosphere. The overall impression is of a typical urban residential block, quiet and orderly, with natural greenery tucked between the buildings.

satellite/000074/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings and open space. In the center of the image, there is a large patch of bare ground surrounded by vegetation and small trees, possibly an underused lot or a construction site. To the left, there are several large, light-colored buildings with flat roofs, arranged in a low, rectangular formation. To the right, the image shows a paved road lined with parked cars, alongside a small, dark green section that looks like a wooded area or small park. The entire scene is captured under overcast conditions, with no shadows visible, indicating a cloudy day. The overall atmosphere is neutral and quiet, with no signs of movement or activity. The image has a slightly grainy quality, suggesting it was taken from a high altitude. The color palette is muted, dominated by grays, browns, and dark greens. There is a sense of stillness and calm in the scene, as if the area is temporarily at rest.

satellite/000075/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings and open land. In the center, there is a large patch of dark green trees and vegetation, surrounded by concrete structures. To the left, a long rectangular building with a flat roof sits above a shadowed space. On the right, a paved road runs vertically, with a few parked cars visible along its edge. Nearby, another building stands with a light-colored roof and open walls. The image is taken from above, showing the layout clearly, but the lighting is flat and gray, suggesting an overcast day. There are no people or vehicles in motion, giving the scene a still and calm feeling. The overall atmosphere is neutral and slightly subdued.

satellite/000075/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings and open space. In the center, there is a large bare patch of land that appears to be cleared or under construction, surrounded by green trees and bushes. To the left, a long building with a flat roof and several windows stands near the edge of the cleared area. On the right, a row of lighter-colored rectangular structures—possibly parking spaces or storage units—runs parallel to a narrow road. A white vehicle is visible on the road near the top right, suggesting some movement but no congestion. The scene is seen from above, with clear visibility and no signs of fog or rain. The lighting appears neutral, suggesting daytime with overcast skies. The overall impression is one of quiet urban function, with no strong emotional tone, just a snapshot of everyday city planning and space use. The structures and open land blend into a calm, neutral environment.

satellite/000075/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with buildings and green spaces. In the center, there is a paved courtyard with a grid-like pattern, surrounded by rectangular structures with flat roofs. To the left, a large dark area appears to be a courtyard or shadowed space with scattered trees. On the right side of the image, a section of an open park or plaza is visible, featuring trees and open land. A narrow road runs along the left edge of the central courtyard, and a small white car is parked near one of the buildings. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with minimal activity visible. The lighting is even and soft, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows. The greenery stands out against the gray tones of the pavement and buildings, adding a touch of natural color. The area has a peaceful, subdued atmosphere, typical of a residential or institutional complex.

satellite/000076/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of paved surfaces and greenery. In the center, a dark, wet street runs vertically, reflecting some light, indicating recent rain. To the left, there is a patch of dense, dark green trees and bushes, possibly a small park or garden. On the right, a large rectangular structure with a patterned roof is visible, likely a parking lot or a covered market. A single white vehicle is parked near the center, standing out against the dark road. The surrounding buildings and structures are mostly gray and brown, suggesting concrete and stone materials. The overall scene appears calm and still, with no visible people or movement. The sky is not visible, but the lighting suggests an overcast day, giving the image a slightly muted tone.

satellite/000076/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a mix of built structures and paved surfaces. In the center, a dark, narrow road cuts vertically through the scene, with a single white vehicle visible near the middle, standing out against the gray pavement. To the left, there is an open space covered with green trees and shrubs, contrasting with the surrounding concrete. On the upper left, a large building with a flat roof and visible columns extends horizontally, while another similar structure lies below it. To the right, a curved, wide area appears to be a parking lot or plaza with light-colored ground, intersected by straight lines forming rectangular sections. The scene is illuminated by daylight, with consistent shadows suggesting a clear sky. The overall impression is one of functional, organized city planning, with no signs of human activity. The image feels still and quiet, like a moment captured from above on a calm day.

satellite/000076/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with surrounding buildings and green space. In the center, a road runs vertically, intersecting with a horizontal street, forming a crossroads. The dividing lines and street markings are visible on the pavement, which appears smooth and light in color. To the left, there is a large polygonal building with a flat roof and rectangular windows, possibly a public or commercial structure. Below it, a patch of dark green trees offers contrast with the concrete. On the right side of the image, a curved structure, likely a curved road or entrance to a park, runs parallel to the intersecting street. Adjacent to it, a series of rectangular plots resembling parking lots or landscaped areas are arranged in rows. The overall scene has a quiet and geometric appearance, with no visible people or vehicles. The image is taken during daylight under clear conditions, with bright, even lighting and minimal shadows. The atmosphere is neutral and orderly, reflecting an organized urban layout. The colors are muted, dominated by grays, browns, and dark greens, contributing to a calm and structured feel.

satellite/000077/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of built and natural elements. At the center is a large rectangular structure that appears to be a parking lot or open plaza, surrounded by paved walkways and faintly visible lines suggesting parking spaces or benches. To the left, a narrow road runs vertically, bordered by a patch of greenery and a small blocky building. On the right, a curved walkway follows the edge of a garden or landscaped zone with trees and shrubs. The overall scene feels calm and orderly, with soft lighting suggesting it was taken on a cloudy day. The lack of people and vehicles contributes to a sense of stillness, like a moment captured before the city stirs to life.

satellite/000077/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of paved surfaces and greenery. In the center, there is a large rectangular courtyard paved with patterned tiles, bordered by a curved walkway on the right. To the left of the courtyard, a narrow road runs vertically with a single vehicle visible on it. On the bottom left, dense trees form a shaded green patch, while on the top left, a building with a flat roof stands near the edge of the frame. The right side of the image shows a curved open space with trees and a small structure amid the pavement. The overall scene appears calm and orderly. The weather is clear, with even lighting suggesting a daytime view. Shadows are soft, indicating no intense sunlight. The scene feels structured and peaceful, like a quiet city park or plaza during a calm moment.

satellite/000077/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of open space and built structures. In the center is a rectangular area with a patterned surface, possibly a plaza or a decommissioned track, bordered by paved walkways and scattered trees. To the right, a wide, curved path leads to a plaza-like space with concentric rings, suggesting a monument or gathering area. This space is framed by low walls and appears largely empty. On the left, there are grassy patches, narrow pathways, and low buildings with flat roofs. A thin grey road cuts through the scene, running vertically in the upper section, with a white vehicle visible near the bottom. The sky is overcast, casting soft, even light with no shadows, giving the image a muted and neutral tone. The lack of people or movement contributes to a still and calm atmosphere, as though captured during a quiet moment in the day. The overall impression is one of order and structure, with a touch of stillness and calm.

satellite/000078/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park with a round central structure and surrounding pathways. In the center, a large, circular feature with radial lines appears to be a fountain or plaza, surrounded by a paved area with greenery. To the left, a long rectangular parking area with clearly marked spaces and a white vehicle is visible. A curved walkway connects the central area to the left side, which is bordered by a patterned stone design and a series of small square plots. The area appears well-maintained but empty, with no people in sight. The lighting suggests an overcast day, with shadows softened and a grayish tone across the scene. The overall impression is calm and orderly, with the structured layout creating a sense of balance and quiet efficiency.

satellite/000078/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a public square or plaza area. In the center, there is a large circular structure with tiered, curved steps that resemble a semi-enclosed amphitheater or seating area. The surface of the structure looks textured, possibly made of stone or concrete, and includes dark circular patterns at the far end. To the left, a narrow street runs vertically, with a white vehicle visible, and the surrounding land is paved with rectangular tiles in a repeating grid pattern. There are patches of greenery along the edges, including bushes and small trees. The entire scene is captured under uniform lighting, suggesting overcast or cloudy weather, with no strong shadows. The image has a calm and orderly feel, with a geometric design that creates a sense of symmetry and control. The absence of people or bright colors gives the place a quiet and still atmosphere, as if it is momentarily empty.

satellite/000078/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a structured urban plaza. In the center, a large circular design dominates the scene, composed of concentric semi-circular elements that resemble steps or tiers. At the center of this circular feature is a small, dark, round focal point, possibly a fountain or monument. Radiating outward from this central area, paved walkways and open spaces create a geometric arrangement. To the left, a series of rectangular sections are visible, likely parking areas or landscaped zones, separated by streets or pathways. The top portion of the image shows a building with a flat roof, and the surrounding area includes designated green spaces with trees. Partially visible structures appear to be modern and functional. The entire scene is marked by symmetry and order, suggesting a planned public space. The lighting is flat and even, indicating an overcast sky or a time of day with no strong shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and organized, with a sense of quiet urban planning. There are no people or moving vehicles, adding to the stillness of the space. The pavement and architectural elements are in clear detail, showing the clean layout of this public area.

satellite/000079/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular plaza with a central fountain. The plaza has concentric stone rings and a paved walkway around the edge. In the center, a tall structure stands in the fountain basin, surrounded by water. To the left, there is a large curved area with steps and greenery. The surrounding area features a grid of streets and buildings, giving a clear sense of urban design. The image is in grayscale, with no visible shadows, suggesting a cloudy or overcast day. The view is calm and ordered, with no people or vehicles in sight. The overall atmosphere is quiet and still, reflecting a peaceful moment in the city.

satellite/000079/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular architectural feature in an urban setting. At the center is a large, symmetrical round structure with concentric rings and semi-circular seating areas, resembling a plaza or fountain. A tall, narrow object—possibly a sculpture or pole—stands in the middle. The surrounding space includes paved walkways with repeating decorative patterns and rows of trees or shrubs, creating a structured and organized layout. To the left, a longer rectangular area with tiered levels suggests a stepped garden or seating section. To the right and above, parts of buildings with flat roofs and open courtyards are visible. The entire scene appears to be in gray tones, indicating a cloudy or overcast day with no strong shadows. The image captures a quiet and orderly public space, seen from above, giving a sense of calm detachment. The uniform design and regular lines create a sense of balance and symmetry. There is no visible movement or people, contributing to a still and peaceful atmosphere. The weather seems mild but overcast, with soft, diffused light covering the area.

satellite/000079/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, symmetrical urban plaza. The central feature is a circular design with concentric rings that resemble a large stone or concrete ring, potentially a fountain or monument, with an open center. Radiating from this core are wide, curved pathways made of light-colored stone or tiled flooring, separated by darker areas, possibly planters or seating. The patterns around the circle form a grid-like layout with intersecting paths. To the left, there is a more defined area with structured rectangular plant beds or possibly parking spaces, bordered by a row of trees. On the right and back parts of the image, a large modern building with flat roof and rectangular windows is visible, suggesting an institutional or governmental structure. The overall scene is evenly lit, with no strong shadows, indicating an overcast sky or diffused sunlight. The area appears orderly, with precise geometry and minimal human presence, creating a calm and structured atmosphere. The dark green patches of landscaping provide contrast to the gray and tan tones of the pavement and building. There is no visible rain or fog, and the image has a clear, high-resolution quality.

satellite/000080/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular courtyard or plaza with a geometric design. To the right, a large curved wall or barrier follows the shape of the walkway, with a smooth, textured surface.
