The lighting is even and soft, with no harsh shadows, indicating either a slightly overcast sky or a time when the sun is not directly overhead. The overall scene is orderly and peaceful, with a sense of quiet urban life.

satellite/000092/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area featuring a wide open plaza and surrounding roads. At the center of the image is a curved, multi-tiered structure resembling a small amphitheater or memorial space, with a flat paved surface and steps leading down. To the right of this structure, a circular plaza with concentric rings and stone paths is visible, partially shaded by trees. On the left side, a grid of city blocks includes patches of green trees and walkways, with a single white car seen on a road running through the blocks. The surrounding sidewalks and parking areas are clearly laid out in a regular pattern. The image appears to be taken during overcast conditions, with even lighting and no strong shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no signs of movement or activity. The scene presents a quiet, structured urban environment, emphasizing symmetry and design in public space.

satellite/000093/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a mix of green spaces, roads, and buildings. In the center, a dark rectangular shape appears to be a pool or water feature, surrounded by trees and paved walkways. To the left, there is a structure with a flat roof, partially shaded, and a narrow path runs nearby. On the right, a wide curved road or plaza encircles the area, bordered by patches of trees and grass. The overall scene is quiet and orderly, with a soft, diffused light suggesting an overcast day. The image carries a calm, neutral atmosphere, with no signs of people or vehicles. The combination of natural and man-made elements gives a balanced, structured feel to the environment.

satellite/000093/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of open spaces and built structures. In the center of the image, there is a paved lot with faint lines, possibly a parking area or a community space, bordered by a curved gray pavement on the right. To the left, a dark green, tree-filled area contrasts with the hard surfaces nearby. Below this green patch, a rectangular block with a patterned surface, likely a courtyard or a modern plaza, extends toward the bottom of the frame. Adjacent to the left is a large, elongated structure with a flat roof that appears to be a public or commercial building. The scene is bathed in soft, even light, indicating a clear day with no shadows cast. The overall atmosphere is quiet and orderly, with no visible movement or people. The combination of open space, greenery, and constructed elements creates a balanced and functional environment, characteristic of a planned city landscape.

satellite/000093/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of open spaces and constructed elements. In the center, a paved pathway runs vertically, dividing the scene into two sides. On the left, there are low buildings with flat roofs and patches of dark green trees, suggesting a park or institutional grounds. A rectangular area bordered by light-colored tiles contains a curved green space, possibly a landscaped garden or small courtyard. To the right, a large curved structure made of light stone rises, resembling a modern amphitheater or public seating area; it is surrounded by a wide clean walkway patterned with geometric designs. Several cars are parked in the top-right section, near another large building. The image appears to be taken during the day under overcast light, giving the scene a neutral grayish tone. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no visible people or movement, conveying a sense of stillness in a structured city environment. The clean lines and spacing suggest careful urban planning, creating a quiet, functional space.

satellite/000094/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban area. In the center, there is a rectangular green space with a curved path and a few trees. To the left, a large dark field or pond stretches across the view, bordered by low greenery. On the right, a parking lot holds a few cars and is next to a building with a flat roof. A narrow road runs along the top edge, separating the green area from a dense, tree-covered zone. The ground appears wet, suggesting recent rain, and the light is flat and gray, giving the scene a calm and subdued mood. There are no people visible, adding to the quiet feel of the area.

satellite/000094/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of buildings, greenery, and paved surfaces. In the center, there is a large open space with trees and bushes, surrounded by concrete structures. To the left, a long low building with a flat roof extends horizontally, and behind it, a taller, more complex structure with multiple sections and a lighter-colored facade is visible. On the right side, a parking lot with marked spaces appears, containing a few vehicles, and next to it, a rectangular building with a dark roof. A narrow road separates parts of the area, and a smaller paved path runs through the green space. The scene is captured under overcast skies, creating a grayish tone across the image with no strong shadows, making details appear flat and muted. The atmosphere is quiet and still, reflecting a typical day in a city without much activity. The overall impression is one of calm functionality, with empty streets and structured layouts suggesting a residential or institutional setting.

satellite/000094/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with a mix of open and built-up areas. In the center, a dark, rectangular patch of water is surrounded by paved surfaces and green spaces with trees and bushes. On the left, there are low, flat-roofed buildings with gray walls and long balconies that appear utilitarian. To the right, a large section of the block consists of a grid of pale, light-colored squares, possibly a parking lot or paved courtyard, bordered by a curved, raised walkway with a few small, repeating structures. A narrow street runs vertically along the right side, with a single white vehicle visible on it. The overall view has a muted, grayish tone, suggesting an overcast day with no direct sunlight. The lack of people or movement gives the scene a calm, almost still atmosphere, like a quiet moment in a typical urban neighborhood. The textures are straightforward—stone, concrete, and greenery—creating a functional, orderly layout.

satellite/000095/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, likely captured during early morning or late afternoon. In the lower part of the image, a building with a rectangular shape and a flat roof sits near a paved surface that appears to be a parking lot or courtyard. To the right of the building, a small green space with hints of trees or shrubs adds a touch of nature. Above, a large patch of darker greenery dominates the upper section, likely a park or tree-filled lot, contrasting with the built environment below. The scene is under soft, diffused light, suggesting mild weather with no strong shadows, contributing to a calm and still atmosphere. The overall view feels peaceful, with minimal movement or activity visible.

satellite/000095/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings and green spaces. In the center of the image is a large patch of grass and trees, appearing dark and leafy, surrounded by structures on all sides. To the top, there is a long building with a flat roof, and to the left, a smaller block with a similar roof style. On the lower part of the image, a long rectangular building with a gray roof extends horizontally, bordered by paved walkways and small tree clusters. To the right, a neat grid of tiled pavement leads to a pathway curving into a shaded area with dense foliage. The area looks well-organized and quiet, with no visible people or vehicles. The sky is overcast, casting soft, even light across the scene, with no shadows or strong contrasts. The overall mood is calm and still, like a peaceful neighborhood captured on a cloudy day.

satellite/000095/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a mix of buildings, roads, and green spaces. In the center, a dark, elongated area appears to be a narrow street or waterway, flanked by structures on both sides. To the left, a series of low-rise buildings with flat roofs are arranged in a row, their surfaces appearing weathered and gray. On the right, a wider paved road runs vertically, bordered by what looks like a parking area with several vehicles. A small patch of greenery—trees and shrubs—lies between the road and some building complexes, offering a contrast to the hard surfaces around it. Above, the buildings stretch into the frame with sharp lines and geometric shapes, suggesting a planned urban layout. The image has a muted color tone, likely due to overcast weather, giving it a calm but slightly cold feel without strong shadows or brightness. The textures of the concrete and foliage are detailed, showing the functional mix of urban life. Overall, the scene feels quiet and orderly, with no signs of movement or people.

satellite/000096/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a flat, urban area with several buildings and a large dark patch in the center. The central object is a black, rectangular feature that looks like a dark pool or a void, surrounded by structures with flat roofs and gray or brown tones. To the left and bottom of this central feature, there are low-rise buildings with straight edges and solid shapes. The right side of the image shows more buildings and some green vegetation, possibly bushes or small trees. The upper section contains more architectural forms, possibly part of a larger development. The image has a dark and muted appearance, with no clear signs of weather conditions like rain or fog. The overall atmosphere feels quiet and still, suggesting a calm moment in a densely built region.

satellite/000096/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a dense urban area, showing rooftops and a central green space. In the center, there is a dark, irregular patch of land covered with trees and shrubs, appearing as a small park or garden. Surrounding this green area are several buildings with flat, gray roofs, likely residential or commercial structures. On the left, a row of low-rise buildings with uniform rooftops extends horizontally. On the right, a larger building with a lighter-colored facade and a grid-like pattern stands out. The image is taken on an overcast day, with diffused light and no strong shadows. The atmosphere is calm and still, with no movement visible on the streets or rooftops. The lack of people or vehicles adds to the quiet and detached feeling of the scene. The overall impression is one of organized urban planning, with the green space providing a contrast to the concrete surroundings.

satellite/000096/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area with many buildings. The central object in the picture is a long, dark body of water, possibly a canal or river, which runs horizontally through the middle of the scene. It divides two sections of developed land. On the left and right sides of the water, there are rectangular buildings with flat roofs, suggesting a planned layout. These buildings are mostly gray and have simple, functional appearances. There are some green areas with trees and bushes around the buildings. To the far right, a grid-like pattern of streets and small blocks is visible. The sky is clear, and the lighting appears to be neutral, indicating an overcast day or midday sun. The overall impression is of a quiet, orderly city area with no visible movement or people. The image feels calm and structured, highlighting the geometry of the urban environment.

satellite/000097/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of an urban area with buildings and a large dark water body. In the center of the image lies the dark, still water, possibly a river or canal, bordered by concrete and stone structures. On the left side, there is a multi-level building with a flat roof and balcony-like features. To the right, a series of curved, stone arches form a bridge or tunnel structure over the water. The buildings and structures are made of gray concrete and stone, giving a functional and solid appearance. The lighting is uniform, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows. The overall impression is calm and orderly, with the dark water contrasting against the light gray buildings. The scene feels quiet and unpopulated.

satellite/000097/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center of the image, a dark, narrow strip of space—possibly a street or a canal—runs horizontally, separating the structures above and below. On the left side, there are several rectangular buildings with flat roofs, appearing gray and plain, suggesting industrial or utilitarian use. The right side features a patch of dense greenery, somewhat irregular and overgrown, adding a natural contrast to the built environment. Above the green space, a large structure with a curved, arched base stands out among the others, its form more distinct against the surrounding muted tones. The picture has a dim and subdued light, indicating overcast weather, with no direct sunlight visible. The overall scene feels calm and slightly bare, lacking human presence, which gives it a still and almost forgotten atmosphere. The tones are mostly gray and dark green, emphasizing the quiet and unchanging nature of the location.

satellite/000097/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of modern and older buildings. In the center, there is a large, dark space that appears to be a courtyard or a solid structure between buildings. On the left side, a rectangular building with a flat roof sits partially in shadow, while to the right, a section of a taller structure with visible window patterns stands out. Below the central space, several large rectangular rooftops extend horizontally, some showing signs of wear and aging. A narrow path or alley can be seen running vertically near the center, adding a sense of depth. The overall scene is quiet and still, with no visible movement or people. The image is captured under overcast skies, giving the scene a muted tone and soft lighting. There are no harsh shadows, indicating a lack of direct sunlight. The colors are mostly shades of gray and brown, contributing to a subdued atmosphere. The greenery seen in patches adds a touch of natural contrast to the built environment. This view presents a calm, almost forgotten corner of the city, where architecture dominates and nature is just visible.

satellite/000098/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings and a dark waterway. The central object is a long body of water, possibly a river, that runs horizontally through the middle of the frame, appearing black and still. On the left side, there is a large structure with a grid-like roof, possibly a covered market or parking lot, with a section that looks like a light-colored walkable bridge. Above this structure, there is a row of smaller buildings or overhangs. To the right of the water, a dark, leafy area suggests a park or green space, and behind it, a taller, darker building with multiple windows is visible. At the bottom of the image, there are more buildings, including a long, flat-roofed structure, likely industrial or commercial. The lighting is neutral, suggestive of an overcast day. The image has a quiet, calm atmosphere with a sense of stillness.

satellite/000098/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area with multiple buildings and pathways. The central part of the image shows a wide, dark roadway running horizontally, bordered by flat-roofed structures. In the upper part of the image, a series of rectangular buildings with gray roofs are aligned closely, forming a blocky pattern. On the left, a lighter gray area with grid-like lines suggests a paved plaza or parking lot. Below the central road, more buildings appear, including one with a curved front and another with a long, rectangular roof. To the right, there are darker patches that might be shaded areas or dense vegetation. The overall appearance is orderly but somewhat flat and uniform, with no visible people or vehicles. The sky above seems clear, as there are no shadows, suggesting an overcast day with even, dim light. The scene feels quiet and still, giving a sense of calm detachment.

satellite/000098/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, structured complex, likely a government or institutional facility. In the center, there is a long building with a flat roof and multiple sections, surrounded by paved areas and what appear to be parking lots. To the left, there is a grid-like pattern of sheltered spaces, possibly for vehicles, and a curved structure, perhaps a driveway or a small ring road. On the right side, a wide open area with darker green patches suggests grass or trees, offering a contrast to the surrounding concrete. A straight road runs horizontally through the middle, dividing the image into upper and lower sections. The lighting is neutral, with no strong shadows, indicating overcast weather or a time of day with diffuse sunlight. The overall atmosphere is orderly and utilitarian, with a clean but impersonal appearance. There is no sign of people or movement, giving the scene a still, almost clinical feel.

satellite/000099/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area featuring a mix of buildings and open spaces. At the center, a wide dark road or pathway runs horizontally, flanked by structures with flat roofs and rectangular layouts. To the left, a grid pattern of paved surfaces and small patches of greenery suggests a parking lot or courtyard area. On the right, a series of curved architectural elements and a large dark shape resembling a basin or pool stand out. The buildings appear gray and utilitarian, with no distinct decorative features. The image is taken in bright daylight, with clear shadows indicating a sunny day. The overall view is orderly and structured, giving a sense of organized city planning, though the uniformity makes the scene feel somewhat stark and impersonal.

satellite/000099/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a large rectangular open area with a grid-like pattern, possibly a parking lot or plaza, surrounded by several low-rise structures. To the left, a curved road runs alongside the area, with a few vehicles visible. On the right, a long building with a flat roof extends across the frame, featuring a series of windows and a few entrance points. Above this building, a larger structure with a stepped roofline stands out, connected by a covered walkway. Smaller green areas with trees are scattered around, providing contrast to the concrete and asphalt. The image shows clear daylight with soft lighting, indicating a partly cloudy or slightly overcast day. Shadows are gentle and elongated, suggesting the time is either morning or late afternoon. The overall impression is calm and orderly, with a focus on functional design and structured layout.

satellite/000099/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a large building complex with a flat roof and multiple rectangular sections. The main structure lies at the center, surrounded by paved areas, including a parking lot with visible grid lines and several cars. To the left of the building is a rounded road intersection with marked crosswalks and a small green space. A curving road separates the parking lot from the building, and a few trees are scattered around the site, providing small patches of green. On the right side of the image, another connected structure appears, slightly lower, with a similar flat roof design. The scene is shown under overcast lighting, with soft, even light and no clear shadows, suggesting a cloudy day. The overall appearance is calm and utilitarian, with little sign of human activity. The colors are muted, dominated by grays, browns, and dark greens, giving the area a quiet, almost subdued atmosphere. This is not a lively urban scene but a structured, functional space likely used for offices or public services.

satellite/000100/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of roads and buildings. At the center, there is a large, light-colored structure surrounded by a network of roads and sidewalks. To the left, a roundabout with white lane markings and a small patch of greenery is visible. Several paved parking lots with grid-like patterns lie to the right and behind the main building. The surrounding streets include crosswalks and curved roads. The atmosphere appears neutral and functional. The image is taken on a clear day, with bright sunlight casting sharp shadows. The overall mood is calm and orderly, typical of a city center during daylight.

satellite/000100/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with a roundabout. The roundabout is in the center, surrounded by paved roads and marked with white crosswalk lines. On the left, a curved road leads into the roundabout, with a few vehicles visible. A large building with a rectangular shape and a grid-like roof sits above the roundabout, partially blocking sunlight. To the right, a long rectangular structure with flat roofing extends along the road, possibly a parking area or a market. Breaks in the pavement and sidewalks connect the roads with the buildings. The image is taken in daylight with clear shadows indicating the sun is high in the sky. There is no sign of rain or fog, and the scene appears calm and orderly, though the lack of visible people or heavy traffic gives it a quiet, static feel. The overall atmosphere is functional and urban, with clean lines and open spaces.

satellite/000100/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, showing a roundabout at the center of the scene, surrounded by roads and marked by white crosswalks. To the left, a large circular traffic island is visible, with curved roads leading into it from multiple directions. The surrounding area features buildings with flat roofs, some with visible rectangular structures and empty parking lots. The buildings are arranged in a pattern that suggests a planned development, possibly a commercial or administrative complex. On the right side of the image, a large structure with multiple levels and a textured facade stands out, likely part of a central facility. The area appears calm and empty, with no visible traffic or people. The sky is overcast, casting a uniform gray light across the scene, with no shadows, indicating flat lighting conditions, possibly due to cloud cover. The ground is mostly paved, with little greenery, and the overall atmosphere is modern and sterile, suggesting an urban environment designed for efficiency rather than aesthetics.

satellite/000101/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout in an urban area. In the center, there is a circular traffic island surrounded by paved roads. A few crosswalks cross the roads leading into and out of the roundabout, and some streets are lined with trees and buildings. On the left side, a parking lot and a structure with a grid pattern are visible, while on the right, a large building with a flat roof and a few parked cars can be seen. The image shows clear conditions with bright sunlight, casting shadows that help distinguish the various shapes and textures. The scene appears calm and orderly, with no visible vehicles or people, giving the area a quiet and structured atmosphere.

satellite/000101/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout at an urban intersection, captured under clear daylight conditions with sharp shadows indicating midday sunlight. The central feature is a large circular roundabout with a dark surface, surrounded by white road markings. Four roads extend from the roundabout, each with crosswalks featuring parallel white stripes. To the left of the roundabout, a paved lot with a rectangular shape appears, possibly a parking space or small field. On the right side, a large structure with a grid-like roof, likely a building or covered area, is visible. Nearby, there are paved pathways and small patches of greenery. The area around the roundabout is quiet and orderly with no visible vehicles or pedestrians, giving it a calm and structured appearance. The scene is composed of gray concrete, dark pavement, and faint greenery, with a precise and functional look, reflecting a well-organized urban environment. The clean, shadowed view suggests clear weather and a neat, controlled setting.

satellite/000101/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection featuring a roundabout at its center. The roundabout is a large circular structure with white markings and is surrounded by roads that curve outward in multiple directions. Several crosswalks cross the roads, creating a grid-like pattern around the roundabout. To the left of the roundabout, a rectangular area with a light-colored surface appears to be a paved space, possibly a parking lot or small plaza. On the right side, there are several buildings with flat roofs, some featuring a yellow or beige tone, and their shadows indicate a bright, clear day. The roads are mostly empty, showing no signs of heavy traffic, which gives the scene a calm and quiet feeling. The buildings are arranged in a structured, organized layout, suggesting this is part of a planned city area. The image quality is sharp, and the cloudless sky suggests good weather conditions, with sunlight casting defined shadows across the scene. There is no visible vegetation, and the dominant colors are gray, black, and beige. Overall, the view feels orderly and detached, capturing a typical moment of stillness in an urban setting.

satellite/000102/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout at an urban intersection. At the center is a circular road with a dark gray surface and a white-painted ring near the middle. Surrounding it are asphalt roads with lane markings and a pedestrian crosswalk to the lower left. To the right, a large building with a grid-like facade stands tall, partially covering a smaller structure below. Near the bottom right, a semi-circular parking area is visible. The scene is captured on an overcast day, with muted colors and no strong shadows, giving the image a somewhat calm and quiet atmosphere. The layout suggests a functional and orderly city space.

satellite/000102/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a roundabout at a major intersection in an urban area, captured under overcast skies that cast a flat, gray light over the scene. At the center of the image is a large circular roundabout with a dark, paved surface and a white line around its edge, surrounded by wide roads with clearly marked crosswalks. Several roadways converge at the roundabout, lined with sidewalks and a grid-like pattern of pavement. To the left, there is a patch of greenery with a few trees and an adjacent open space that appears to be a sports field or small park. On the right, there is a complex of modern buildings with flat roofs, some featuring glass surfaces that reflect the muted light. There are no visible vehicles or people, giving the scene a quiet and still atmosphere despite the complex layout. Near the bottom, a curved road draws the eye outward, leading away from the central intersection. The overall impression is one of order and structure, with no sign of movement or activity, suggesting a moment of calm in the daily rhythm of city life. The image feels detached and slightly sterile, emphasizing the engineered nature of the environment.

satellite/000102/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection featuring a roundabout at the center. The roundabout is surrounded by multiple crosswalks and roads, with vehicles visible on the surrounding roads. To the left of the roundabout, there is a rectangular section with a sports court, possibly for tennis or basketball, surrounded by a light-colored border. On the right side, several buildings are visible, including a large structure with a flat roof and a smaller curved building. A series of sidewalks and parking areas are located near the buildings. The image is taken during daylight, with neutral sunlight casting short shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly with no signs of congestion or movement. The streets are well-defined, and the layout suggests a planned city environment. The scene is slightly desaturated, giving it a more subdued and functional appearance. There are no people or animals visible, and the presence of greenery is minimal, primarily along the edges of the terrain. The image conveys a sense of routine and urban functionality.

satellite/000103/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with buildings and roads. In the center, a large paved area with a grid-like pattern is surrounded by dark asphalt roads. To the left, a circular road with a white line curves around, leading to a crosswalk at the bottom left. On the right, several rectangular buildings of different sizes line the edge of the scene. A curved, light-colored structure runs along the bottom right, possibly a ramp or walkway. Trees and small shrubs are scattered near the road and between buildings. The image appears to have been taken on a cloudy day, with flat lighting and no strong shadows, giving the scene a gray and quiet look.

satellite/000103/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of roads, buildings, and open spaces. In the center, there is a large paved area that appears to be a parking lot or plaza, with rows of rectangular rectangles likely being parking spaces. To the left, a roundabout with a white circle in the middle is visible, surrounded by a bike path and a road with crosswalks. The roads seem curving and intersecting, forming a web-like pattern. On the right side, a long and wide industrial-looking building with a flat roof stands out, next to a smaller structure. Several trees or shrubs are visible, although sparse, near the roads and buildings. The image was taken during daylight with clear visibility and no signs of rain, fog, or shadows; sunlight seems evenly spread across the scene. The overall atmosphere is neutral and functional, conveying the sense of a structured but impersonal city environment. The tone is calm and orderly, with no human presence or activity visible.

satellite/000103/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a roundabout and several buildings. In the center-left, the roundabout is clearly visible with a circular road surrounded by a narrow traffic island; white crosswalks lead into the intersection from the top and bottom. To the right of the roundabout, a large rectangular structure with a flat roof and long rows of windows dominates the scene, appearing to be a public or institutional building. Surrounding this building are paved areas and open spaces. A curving road runs from the bottom left toward the center, creating a smooth transition into the roundabout. There is a smaller, curved segment of road in the lower middle section, partially obscured by shadows. The entire scene is captured under soft, diffused light, suggesting an overcast day, with no strong shadows indicating direct sunlight. The image conveys a sense of calm order, with the geometric layout of roads and buildings adding a structured feel. All elements are clearly defined, though the tone is muted by the gray tones of the pavement and structures. The overall atmosphere is quiet and uneventful, typical of a cityscape in daylight.

satellite/000104/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with large buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a rectangular structure with a flat roof and a small protruding section on the top right. To the left, a large building with a grid-like pattern of windows stands tall, and below it is a curved, white-edged area that may be a driveway or plaza. On the right, another long, low building extends horizontally, partially shaded by the surrounding structures. The buildings appear dark and heavy under the overcast sky, creating a cool, muted atmosphere. The image lacks bright colors, with grey and black tones dominating the scene. There is no sign of people or vehicles, giving the area a quiet and still feel. The weather seems cloudy, with no shadows or sunlight visible.

satellite/000104/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, dark building complex surrounded by paved areas and green spaces. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, located near the center of the frame. To the left of the building, there is a curved, covered walkway leading to a smaller structure with a sloped roof. Behind the main building, several vehicles are parked in a lot, partially visible through a tall fence. On the upper left, a paved plaza with a grid pattern stretches out, while a narrow road runs along the lower left edge, bordered by trees. The surrounding area includes patches of grass and shrubs, giving a slight contrast to the dense gray concrete. The image is taken during the day under bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows. The atmosphere appears calm and orderly, yet the overall muted color palette and lack of visible people give it a quiet and slightly solemn feel.

satellite/000104/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, showing a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, a large asphalt parking lot is surrounded by low, rectangular buildings with flat roofs. To the left, a curved road runs alongside a small traffic island with a faint sidewalk pattern. The space between the buildings feels clean and organized, with a few narrow walkways leading through the area. On the right side, a taller structure stands slightly apart from the others, adding vertical contrast to the mostly horizontal layout. The image is captured on a clear day, under bright, even lighting that casts soft shadows, suggesting midday conditions. There are no people or vehicles visible, giving the scene a calm and still atmosphere. The muted gray tones of the pavement and rooftops dominate, with occasional patches of green that hint at small landscaping efforts. Overall, the environment appears functional and uncluttered, reflecting a purposeful design with minimal decoration.

satellite/000105/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a dense urban area with several buildings. In the center, there is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof, which appears to be a warehouse or a commercial building, surrounded by other smaller structures. To the left, a tall building with a grid-like facade stands out, while to the right, a low stone wall and narrow passage can be seen. The area appears to be quiet, with no visible people or vehicles. The image was likely captured during overcast weather, as the lighting is flat and the colors are muted, with shades of gray dominating the scene. There are no signs of rain or fog, but the atmosphere feels subdued and still.

satellite/000105/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with several buildings and paved surfaces. In the center, there is a long rectangular structure that appears to be a low wall or retaining structure, surrounded by dark paved spaces and smaller buildings. To the left, a curved section with a railing and a small parking area is visible, with a few vehicles parked nearby. Above this, a grid-like pattern of a parking lot or courtyard can be seen, with clear boundaries and some greenery. On the right, a larger building with a flat roof occupies a significant portion of the frame, adjacent to open paved areas. The overall image is dark and lacks fine detail, suggesting it may have been captured during cloudy weather or at a time of low light, possibly early morning or late evening. The structures appear static and unoccupied, creating a quiet and still atmosphere. The image has a muted color palette, dominated by grays, blacks, and faint browns, with minimal signs of activity. To the left, a curved concrete structure is visible, possibly a pathway or a small wall. On the right, a large rectangular building with a flat roof stands next to the green area. Above, a grid of square tiles covers a paved surface, likely part of a courtyard or plaza. The image appears to have been taken on an overcast day, with soft, even lighting and no shadows. The overall scene feels calm and slightly muted, with a quiet, urban atmosphere.

satellite/000118/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, viewed from above. In the center, a patch of small trees and shrubs creates a green space, surrounded by gray pavement and buildings. To the left, a curved wall or low structure follows a gentle arc, possibly part of a plaza or park design. The main area features a grid of steps or tiled patterns, creating a patterned architectural surface. To the right and bottom, a large concrete building with flat roof and minimal details stands prominently. The overall scene appears calm and quiet, with no visible people or vehicles, giving a sense of stillness. The area looks slightly shadowed, suggesting an overcast sky or the position of the sun. There is a presence of water, possibly a small pond or water feature, near the center. The image is marked with date and copyright text, common in satellite views. The streets and surfaces appear clean, but the imagery has a muted tone, lacking strong colors. The atmosphere feels neutral, neither warm nor cold, but steady and ordered, characteristic of a planned city space.

satellite/000118/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with geometric landscaping and surrounding structures. In the center, there is a large paved surface made up of square tiles arranged in a grid pattern, which appears to be a plaza or courtyard. To the left of this grid, a curved walkway made of large stone slabs forms part of a larger landscaped design, incorporating a semi-circular structure that might be a small amphitheater or seating area. On the right side of the image, a grassy area with scattered trees borders a paved path, and a building with a flat roof is visible at the lower right. The upper right includes a roundabout or circular road with a small structure at its center. The scene is viewed under overcast lighting, giving it a flat, muted tone. There are no people or vehicles in sight, which contributes to a calm and still atmosphere. The image has a slightly blurred quality, possibly due to weather conditions or cloud cover. The overall setting feels tranquil and orderly, with a balanced mix of natural greenery and man-made forms.

satellite/000119/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of greenery and structures. In the center, there is a paved section with a grid-like pattern, possibly a walkway or parking lot, surrounded by dense dark green trees. To the left, a curved concrete edge, perhaps part of a road or a low wall, curves gently into the frame. On the right, a large light-colored building with a flat roof stands prominently, showing minimal architectural detail. A narrow path or lane runs vertically between the trees and the building. There are no visible people or vehicles. The sky is overcast, creating a soft, diffused light and casting subtle shadows. The area gives a calm, slightly empty impression, with the gray and green tones contributing to a subdued, still atmosphere.

satellite/000119/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a mix of buildings and greenery. In the center, a rectangular structure with a flat roof and a grid-like pattern is visible, possibly a small commercial or residential building. To the right, a larger building with a wooden deck or balcony stands out, suggesting a more modern design. On the left, a curved pathway or road winds through a dense patch of trees, adding a natural contrast to the man-made structures. The area is shaded heavily, likely due to cloud cover, giving the scene a muted and subdued tone. The image appears slightly blurry, possibly due to atmospheric conditions or low resolution. While there are no visible people or vehicles, the layout hints at a modest, possibly residential neighborhood. The overall atmosphere is calm and still, with the surrounding greenery softening the hard lines of the buildings. The lighting is flat and even, indicating an overcast day with no direct sunlight. There are no signs of rain, but the lack of shadows suggests thick clouds overhead.

satellite/000119/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings and greenery. In the center of the image, there is a large open space with a parking lot made of dark and light squares, possibly a courtyard or a small public area. To the left, a curved path runs alongside a grassy section and a few trees, leading toward a round structure that might be a fountain or a designated gathering point. On the right, a rectangular building with a flat roof stands out, showing signs of wear with patches of discoloration. Adjacent to it is a smaller structure, possibly a garage or storage room. In the lower part of the image, a larger building with visible windows and a small rooftop detail, such as vents, anchors the scene. The area is shaded, suggesting an overcast or cloudy day, with no direct sunlight visible. The overall impression is one of quiet urban planning with a blend of built and natural elements. The green areas are dense, indicating well-maintained vegetation, while the structures appear functional. There is a sense of calm, possibly even solitude, with no movement or human activity apparent from above. The details in the image are clear, but the absence of bright colors or bright lighting gives the scene a subdued appearance.

satellite/000120/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of greenery and structures. In the center, a dense cluster of dark green trees forms a small park or shrubbery patch. To the left, a paved pathway curves through the scene, bordered by stone or concrete edges, leading toward a possibly circular or diagonal walkway that extends into the upper left. On the right, a portion of a building is visible, with a light-colored wall and a patterned or tiled section that suggests a courtyard or enclosed space. The overall tone of the image is muted, with grayscale and dark tones dominating, suggesting the photo was taken under overcast skies with little sunlight. No people or vehicles are visible, giving the scene a still and subdued atmosphere, as if captured during a hazy morning or in the soft light after rain.

satellite/000120/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area featuring a mix of green spaces and urban structures. In the upper left, a circular plaza with a symmetrical design and paved pathways stands out, surrounded by low walls and small green patches. To the right of the plaza, a dense cluster of trees creates a dark, leafy area, likely a park or garden. The lower right shows part of a building, possibly residential or commercial, with a flat roof and a small balcony. A narrow walkway or road runs along the bottom edge, connecting different sections of the area. The image appears to be taken during the day, under overcast skies, as the lighting is even and lacks strong shadows. There is no visible movement, giving the scene a calm and static quality. The overall impression is one of quiet urban planning, where nature and built environments coexist in a balanced but unremarkable way.

satellite/000120/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block showing a mix of greenery and urban structures. In the lower center of the image, there is a dense patch of dark green trees forming a small park. To the left, a large curved structure with concentric stone rings around a central point—likely a circular plaza or monument—stands out due to its geometric design and light-colored surface. A few buildings with flat roofs are visible on the right side, some of which appear modern and others more utilitarian, with one showing a grid-like rooftop pattern. A paved pathway or road runs through the top of the image, connecting the structures. The overall scene is captured under clear, well-lit conditions with no sign of rain or fog. The image has a quiet and orderly atmosphere, with the blend of nature and urban design presenting a balanced, organized cityscape. There is no visible movement or people, giving the scene a calm and still feel.

satellite/000121/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular stone structure, likely a public plaza or monument. At the center is a gray, tiered platform with a possible fountain or pavilion, surrounded by steps and walkways. To the left, there are rectangular stone sections with inset patterns, possibly benches or reserved areas. A tree-covered green space occupies the right side, with a darker path leading toward the structure. The image appears to be taken on an overcast day, as shadows are soft and the lighting is flat. The overall atmosphere is calm and still, reflecting a quiet urban or park setting. The grayscale tones give it a neutral, almost muted feel. The scene lacks any people or vehicles, adding to the tranquil, deserted mood.

satellite/000121/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular architectural structure, likely a plaza or monument, surrounded by greenery and pathways. The central feature is a large, multi-tiered circular design with open spaces and radiating walkways, resembling a modern sculpture or memorial. To the left, a long, narrow building with rectangular windows runs parallel to the structure. On the right, dense trees and shrubs form a dark, natural border, contrasting with the man-made design. Smaller paved areas and possible seating zones are visible around the edges. The image shows no people, giving it a still, quiet feel. The lighting appears flat and even, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows. The overall scene has a calm, orderly atmosphere, with the gray stone and dark foliage creating a somber tone. There is no sign of movement or activity, enhancing the sense of stillness. This space feels functional and designed, possibly a public area meant for gatherings or reflection.

satellite/000121/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular public space, likely a plaza or monument, captured from above on a cloudy day. At the center of the image is a large, rounded structure resembling a fountain or sculpture, surrounded by concentric stone rings and steps, creating a radial design. The central area is dark, possibly due to shadows or water, with lighter stone pathways extending outward in segments. To the left of the central feature, there is a long, straight walkway with symmetrical, rectangular planters or small structures arranged along its length. The right side of the image includes a dense area of green trees providing contrast to the stone and paved sections. On the right, a grid-like pattern of small, square features—possibly a garden or paved section—can be seen, leading toward a cluster of buildings in the bottom-right corner. The overall scene has a muted color palette, with gray and brown tones dominating due to the weather and materials. The lack of people or movement gives the space a still and quiet atmosphere, enhanced by the overcast sky and the abstract, geometric layout of the site.

satellite/000122/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular structure that resembles a monument or an observatory, viewed from above. At the center is a large, dark circular area with concentric rings, possibly a basin or pavement, surrounded by tiered stone steps or platforms. Four symmetrical sections extend outward from the center, each with a square grid pattern and small rectangular openings, suggesting gates or architectural features. The structure is made of light gray stone and appears in good condition. On the outer edges, dark green vegetation is visible, especially on the lower left and right sides, indicating the presence of trees or bushes. The image is taken in daylight with even lighting, and there is no fog or rain. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with the design showing symmetry and balance. The scene feels still and peaceful, with no signs of movement or activity.

satellite/000122/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular architectural structure, resembling a plaza or monument, viewed from above. At the center is a large, round platform with concentric rings and a central feature that appears to be a fountain or sculpture. Radiating outward from the center are curved pathways that divide the space into sections, with rows of trees or planted areas situated in each segment. On the left and right sides of the image, dense green trees form borders around the structure, creating a natural frame. The surrounding area appears paved or landscaped, with visible pathways leading into and out of the space. The overall color tone is muted, suggesting overcast or cloudy weather, with soft, diffused lighting and no strong shadows. The image gives a sense of calm and order, emphasizing symmetry and planned design. The environment feels quiet and structured, with no visible people or vehicles, adding to the stillness of the scene.

satellite/000122/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular public square or monument, viewed from above. At the center of the image is a large, symmetrical structure with concentric rings and a central dome-like feature, possibly a fountain or sculpture. Radiating from the center are straight pathways that extend outward, dividing the space into multiple sections. These pathways are bordered by low walls and paved areas with rectangular patterns. On the left and right sides of the image, dense clusters of trees surround the structure, creating a green border. The overall scene has a somber, muted tone due to the grayish-purple lighting, which suggests either early morning or overcast weather. The sky is not visible, but the lack of shadows and the even lighting imply cloudy conditions. The area appears quiet and empty, with no people or vehicles visible, giving it a still and orderly atmosphere. The texture of the ground is mostly smooth, with slight details in the paving stones and shadows along the edges of the structure. The image captures a sense of planned symmetry and spatial organization, typical of urban design focused on visibility and movement.

satellite/000123/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular, symmetrical structure resembling a large plaza or monument. At the center is a round area with concentric rings and a small object in the middle, possibly a fountain or statue. Radiating from the center are several stone pathways that divide the space into segments, each containing square openings and smaller decorative features. On the left and right sides of the structure, there are darker patches that appear to be trees or planted areas, providing contrast to the light-colored stone. The surrounding area is paved, with visible shadows suggesting the sun is high in the sky. The image has a muted color palette, with gray and green tones dominating. The overall view is still and orderly, giving a calm and balanced impression. The weather appears clear and dry, with no clouds or rain visible.

satellite/000123/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, circular monument or memorial space, viewed from directly above. The central feature is a grand, tiered structure with concentric rings and a domed or circular top section, suggesting an architectural design meant to symbolize unity or importance. Radiating outward from the center are several stone pathways or bridges that connect to outer platforms or quadrants, each containing smaller buildings or enclosed areas. These platforms extend in four main directions—north, south, east, and west—giving the structure a balanced, symmetrical appearance. The entire complex is surrounded by a wide moat or water feature, visible as a dark, smooth ring that encircles the base of the structure. On the outer edges, particularly in the lower half of the image, dense clusters of trees and greenery provide a natural contrast to the stone and concrete elements. The pavement and structures are light gray, and the overall lighting is even and soft, indicating an overcast day with no harsh shadows. The scene feels calm and orderly, with a sense of intentional design and quiet grandeur, rather than bustling activity. No people or vehicles are visible, adding to the stillness of the location.

satellite/000123/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, circular architectural structure, likely a monument or plaza, seen from directly above. The central object is a wide, flat, stone-like platform with concentric rings and a central raised area resembling a fountain or sculpture. Radiating from the center are several wide pathways or walkways that divide the space into sections. Each of these sections contains small rectangular features that may be benches or planters. The surrounding perimeter is bordered by a short wall or low barrier, beyond which lies a ring of green trees that encircles the entire site. On the outer edges, more trees and dark green patches suggest landscaping or parkland. The overall view is symmetrical and geometric, giving the site a formal, planned appearance. The lighting appears even and dim, suggesting an overcast day or late afternoon with no strong shadows. There is no visible activity or people, contributing to a calm and still atmosphere. The image has a monochrome tone, emphasizing the texture of the stone and the regularity of the design. The lack of movement and absence of bright colors gives the scene a quiet, almost solemn feel.

satellite/000124/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, circular public space, possibly a monument or memorial. At the center is a dark, concentric structure resembling a tiered basin or fountain, surrounded by wide, light-colored stone walkways that radiate outward. A straight path extends from the center toward the bottom of the frame, lined with small, evenly spaced rectangular features that may be windows or openings in a wall. To the left, a darker, irregularly shaped area with dense greenery suggests a garden or wooded section. The image has a muted, overcast tone, with no strong shadows, indicating cloudy or diffuse lighting. The scene appears calm and quiet, with a sense of symmetry and order in the layout. The overall atmosphere is still and subdued, with no visible people or movement.

satellite/000124/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular plaza or monument, likely a public square or memorial. The central feature is a large circular structure with concentric rings and pathways, resembling a sunburst or star pattern. A long, straight walkway extends from the center toward the bottom of the image, flanked by symmetrical sections with square-tiled areas and small plantings. On the left side, there is a patch of greenery with trees and shrubs, while the right side appears more paved with geometrically arranged spaces. The surrounding area has a mix of paved and grassy zones, with some structural elements visible along the edges. The image has a muted, grayish tone, suggesting overcast weather with no clear shadows. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with a sense of symmetry and design in the layout. The overall mood is quiet and reflective, emphasizing the scale and structure of the space rather than movement or human activity.

satellite/000124/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a circular architectural structure, likely a monument or public gathering space, viewed from above. At the center of the image is a large, circular platform with concentric rings and a raised, dome-like feature in the middle, which appears to be a fountain or sculpture. Surrounding this central feature are evenly spaced wedge-shaped sections resembling steps or seating areas, forming a radial pattern. A straight pathway extends downward from the center, connecting the circular structure to a lower area of the site. On the left side of the image, there is a rectangular area with a grid-like surface, possibly a paved plaza or parking lot, bordered by green trees. The right side shows more greenery and a smaller arrangement of structures, possibly benches or informational signs. The overall color palette is muted, with shades of gray and dark green dominating the scene. The image appears to be taken on an overcast day, with no strong shadows or bright light, giving it a subdued and calm atmosphere. The lack of visible people adds to the quiet, still feeling of the place.

satellite/000125/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park area with a curved stone structure at the center-right, which appears to be part of a large circular fountain or monument with steps and concentric rings. To the left, there is a section with a paved walkway and scattered trees, forming a shaded, green space. In the upper left corner, more trees and bushes create a dense, natural-looking patch. The image shows no people or moving objects. The lighting is even, suggesting a clear day with no visible clouds or shadows. The overall look is neat and organized, showing a well-maintained area, but the low resolution gives it a slightly blurred, textbook-like quality.

satellite/000125/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban park or plaza. In the center, there is a large circular structure with concentric rings and steps, resembling a fountain or monument. To the left of this central feature, a paved pathway curves through areas of dense green trees and shrubs. On the right side, a wide open space with long, straight walkways and a grid-like pattern of tiles is visible. Small rectangular patches, possibly benches or planters, are placed along the edges of the plaza. The overall design is geometric and orderly, with a mix of natural and man-made elements. The bright lighting and clear shadows suggest sunny weather during the day. The image has a clean, structured feel, giving it a calm and well-maintained appearance. There are no people or vehicles, adding to the stillness of the scene. Overall, the space looks peaceful and designed for walking or gathering.

satellite/000125/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban park with a prominent circular structure at its center. The central object is a wide, circular plaza with concentric rings and central patterns, resembling a sundial or monument, made of light-colored stone or concrete. Radiating from this plaza are symmetrical pathways, some flanked by dark green trees and shrubs, creating a clean geometric layout. To the left of the plaza, there is a grid-like section with paved paths and rectangular green spaces, possibly a garden or public seating area. The right side features a long, narrow walkway lined with vertical rectangular planters or benches. The surrounding area includes more greenery and open spaces, with a few small buildings visible in the lower left corner. The image has a muted, monochromatic tone, possibly due to overcast weather, with soft shadows suggesting diffused daylight. The scene conveys a sense of order and calm, with the design emphasizing symmetry and balance, giving it a formal, almost meditative quality. The overall atmosphere is quiet and structured, reflecting a well-planned public space.

satellite/000126/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park area with a mix of paved pathways and green landscaping. In the center, there is a curved stone path surrounded by trees and shrubs, forming a natural and calm space. To the left, a grid-like pattern of light-colored tiles and rectangular structures suggests a plaza or open seating area, possibly with benches. On the right, another curved pathway extends outward, connecting to the main path. The vegetation appears dense and healthy, mostly dark green, indicating well-maintained grounds. There are no people visible, adding to the quiet and still atmosphere. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a clear day with no clouds. The overall impression is peaceful and orderly, with a sense of balance between nature and human design.

satellite/000126/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a park area with paved walkways and greenery. In the center, there is a circular structure with a path that looks like a small amphitheater or plaza, surrounded by trees and open space. To the left of the circle, a rectangular grid of concrete blocks is visible, segmented into several sections that possibly serve as seating or bordered garden areas. There is a narrow path running vertically through the image, connecting the central circle to the upper and lower parts of the frame. On the left side, a few buildings are partially visible, tucked at the edge of the green space. The image is taken during daylight, with clear visibility and no signs of rain or fog. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, presenting a quiet outdoor area with a geometric layout typical of urban parks. Trees and shrubs are spaced throughout, providing shade over parts of the walkways. The lighting is flat, indicating an overcast or middle-of-day sky, and the colors are dominated by greens, grays, and browns, giving the scene a neutral, functional tone.

satellite/000126/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a large, curved public space with a paved walkway and scattered greenery. At the center of the scene, there is a circular structure with tiered levels, possibly a stage or amphitheater, surrounded by a wide path. To the left, rectangular blocks of land are arranged in a grid pattern, with some areas covered in trees and others open and bare. These plots are separated by narrow roads or pathways. In the bottom left corner, several rectangular buildings with flat roofs are visible, likely residential or commercial structures. The top left shows a section of dense vegetation and scattered smaller buildings. The image has a grayish tone, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows or sunlight. The overall layout appears organized and functional, with a mix of natural and built elements. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, reflecting a quiet section of the city.

satellite/000127/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a paved area with geometric patterns, likely a courtyard or plaza. The central structure is flanked by open walking paths with grid-like designs and bordered by darker green trees on the right and lower sides. On the left, a building with a flat roof and a small white section is visible. A curved pathway arcs along the right edge, suggesting a park or garden area. The image appears clear and sharp, indicating a sunny day with bright lighting and no clouds or fog. The overall scene looks structured and peaceful, typical of a planned urban space.

satellite/000127/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a structured outdoor area, likely part of a campus or public park. In the center of the image, there is a large, open courtyard paved with light-colored tiles arranged in a grid pattern. In the middle of the courtyard, a dark, geometric-shaped garden plot is visible, surrounded by paved walkways. To the left of the central space, a long rectangular building with a flat roof extends horizontally, featuring several windows and a small entrance section. On the right side, a curved pathway follows the edge of the scene, bordered by dense clusters of trees and shrubs with dark green foliage, adding a natural contrast to the geometric layout. A smaller paved section with a distinct, irregularly shaped planter is located below the central garden area. The image is captured from a high, top-down angle, and the overall scene appears calm and orderly, with no signs of people or movement. The lighting is even and soft, indicating an overcast day with no direct sunlight or shadows. The atmosphere is quiet and serene, with a strong sense of balance between the natural and constructed elements.

satellite/000127/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of buildings, pathways, and green spaces. At the center, there is a large open plaza paved with square tiles, arranged in a grid pattern, forming a wide, light-colored walkway that leads to a small, dark rectangular structure at the far end. To the left of the plaza, a long, rectangular building with a flat roof stands adjacent to a narrow tree-lined strip. On the right, a curved roadway appears, bordered by dense dark green trees and a low, smooth concrete wall. The surrounding greenery is lush, with clusters of trees and shrubs providing contrast to the engineered landscape. The image is captured under overcast skies, with soft, diffused lighting that gives the scene a calm and muted tone. The overall impression is one of organized simplicity, with no visible people or vehicles, suggesting a moment of stillness in a structured environment.

satellite/000128/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet, structured outdoor space, possibly a courtyard or part of a park. In the center, there is a paved area with a grid pattern, surrounded by dark green trees and shrubs. To the left, a long, low building with a flat roof extends horizontally, and a smaller rectangular structure lies beneath it. On the right, a shaded area contains mounds of earth, possibly a small garden or landscaping. At the bottom of the frame, a portion of another building with a sloped roof appears. satellite/000128/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center, a rectangular courtyard is surrounded by paved walkways and bordered by dense trees. On the left, a long white building with a flat roof stands near another smaller structure, both appearing calm and still. To the right, a large green space with bushes and trees fills a section of the frame. There are no visible people or movement, giving the scene a peaceful and unpopulated appearance. The lighting suggests it is a cloudy day, with soft shadows and no bright sunlight. The colors are muted—gray concrete, dark green foliage, and light-colored walls—contributing to the calm and orderly mood. The image gives the impression of a well-planned section of a city, possibly a park or campus, where nature and buildings coexist in quiet balance.

satellite/000128/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with buildings and open spaces. This area is surrounded by trees and greenery, with darker patches of foliage visible along the right side and bottom. To the left, a long, low building with a dark roof extends horizontally across the frame, with smaller structures nearby. The architecture appears modern and functional, with flat rooftops and clean lines. The ground is mostly gray and light brown, showing a mix of concrete and possibly dirt paths. The image has a muted, neutral color tone, suggesting an overcast day with no strong sunlight or shadows. There is no visible movement or people, giving the scene a calm and still atmosphere. The overall impression is one of quiet order, where design and nature coexist in a balanced, structured layout.

satellite/000129/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a built environment, showing a complex of structures from above. satellite/000129/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a group of modern buildings with flat roofs. The central object is a long, rectangular structure with a dark gray roof, surrounded by other buildings with similar design, forming a complex layout. To the right, there is an open courtyard with a grid pattern of light-colored pavement and a curved, dark green area that appears to be a garden or landscaped section. On the left, additional structures are visible, partially shaded and connected by covered walkways. Above the shaded areas, some green vegetation can be seen, including trees that form a natural border around the complex. The scene is viewed under clear conditions, with sharp contrasts between the dark roof surfaces and lighter pavement. The overall impression is one of geometric order and quiet functionality, with no signs of movement or people. The architectural style is utilitarian, emphasizing clean lines and practical shapes. There is little to suggest activity; the area appears calm and empty. The lighting is neutral, indicating a daytime view without strong shadows or sunlight, possibly under overcast conditions. The image conveys a sense of stillness and control, as if captured during a moment of minimal human presence.

satellite/000129/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a cluster of buildings and open spaces, likely a campus or institutional complex. The main structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof and a light-colored exterior, positioned near the center of the image. To the left of this building is a smaller, block-shaped structure, possibly a utility or maintenance building. On the right, a paved area with a grid pattern appears to be a walkway or parking lot, bordered by greenery and a larger, leafy tree that provides a natural contrast to the surrounding hard surfaces. The area behind the main building contains several levels of landscaping and pathways, with lower platforms and shaded walkways indicating a deliberate design for pedestrian movement. The overall environment appears orderly and functional, with a neutral color palette consisting of grays, greens, and earth tones. The image is taken during daylight with clear visibility, suggesting a calm, sunny day with no clouds or precipitation. There is no movement or human activity visible, giving the scene a quiet, still atmosphere.

satellite/000130/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a building complex viewed from above. In the center, a long, rectangular structure with a flat roof dominates the scene, connected by walkways to other sections. To the left, a larger block with a darker roof has vertical lines suggesting windows or divisions. On the right, a smaller, lighter-colored building stands adjacent to the main structure. Below the central roof, a shadowed area hints at a courtyard, bordered by darker green shapes likely from trees. The overall impression is of a functional layout, possibly institutional or commercial. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a sunny day with no clouds or fog, but the image has a cool, neutral tone with no strong emotional color. The scene feels orderly and still.

satellite/000130/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, likely a residential or institutional complex, captured from above. The central focus is a large, rectangular building with a flat roof and a light-colored facade, surrounded by other structures of similar architectural style. To the left, a long, low building extends horizontally, with a series of windows and a segmented design along its length. On the right, a grid-like pattern of pavement and possibly a parking area is visible, suggesting a structured outdoor space.
