There is no sign of people or movement, giving the image a calm and quiet atmosphere. The dominant colors are gray, green, and the dark tone of the main building. The image is clean and well-lit, with no clouds or signs of rain. Overall, the area looks well-maintained and designed for a public or institutional purpose.

satellite/000425/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, likely a central city block, captured in bright daylight with clear skies. The central object is a tall, dark rectangular building with a flat roof, standing prominently on the right side of the frame. To its left is a large open space with a geometric pattern of light-colored concrete or stone, possibly a plaza or public square, containing rectangular and square sections that resemble gardens or small ponds. Along the edges of the plaza, some greenery and small trees are visible. On the left side of the image, a curved structure or ramp leads toward the square, bordered by rows of evenly spaced landscaping. A few small vehicles can be seen near the building, suggesting light activity. The layout is orderly and symmetrical, giving the scene a clean, structured, and functional appearance. The surrounding roads and pathways are wide and well-maintained, contributing to a sense of urban planning and organization. The overall atmosphere is calm and uncluttered, with no signs of heavy traffic or crowds.

satellite/000426/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, showing a wide, open plaza with a long rectangular structure in the center, likely a building or covered walkway. A long, linear pool or water feature runs parallel to the structure, bordered by low walls and pathways. To the left, there is a pedestrian walkway bordered by a row of evenly spaced trees or shrubs. On the right, a taller building with glass windows stands beside the plaza. The scene has a clean, organized appearance, with light-colored pavement and dark green landscaping providing contrast. The sky appears overcast, casting a soft, even light with no sharp shadows, giving the image a calm and structured atmosphere. The area looks quiet, not crowded, and well-maintained.

satellite/000426/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, symmetrical building complex with a central courtyard. The main structure is rectangular and appears to be made of light-colored stone or concrete, with a flat roof and multiple levels. The courtyard in the center is green and landscaped, surrounded by long, narrow walkways and small green areas. On the left side of the building, there is a large parking area with several vehicles, and a driveway leads into the complex. On the right side, a tall, dark building stands in contrast to the rest of the complex, possibly a tower or a modern addition. The surrounding area includes paved roads, sidewalks, and some green trees along the borders. The image shows clear daylight, with shadows indicating the sun is relatively high in the sky. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no people or moving vehicles visible. The image has a clean, geometric feel, suggesting a well-planned and maintained environment.

satellite/000426/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, structured outdoor area, likely a public plaza or memorial site. At the center is a rectangular space with tiered, stepped edges, possibly a fountain or dry water feature, surrounded by paved walkways. Rows of small, uniformly spaced planters or benches line the edges, forming a geometric pattern. To the right, a dark, tall building with a flat roof stands, partially blocking the view. On the left, a more open, lighter-colored area with dense greenery suggests a park-like zone, contrasting with the rigid design of the central structure. A paved road runs along the upper edge of the frame, with a few vehicles visible, hinting at urban surroundings. The scene is captured under clear, bright daylight, with sharp shadows indicating a sunny day. The overall impression is one of order and design, balanced between natural and built environments, without emotional overtones. The landscape shows careful planning, emphasizing symmetry and functionality in an urban setting.

satellite/000427/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a public square or plaza, captured on a clear day with bright sunlight. In the center, there is a large rectangular area surrounded by a patterned walkway made of light-colored tiles, arranged in neat horizontal lines. To the left, a tall, dark building stands vertically, casting a shadow across part of the plaza. The edges of the square are bordered by rows of low green shrubs and a wide sidewalk with evenly spaced planters. The layout appears orderly and spacious, suggesting a place meant for walking or gatherings. The overall scene feels calm and structured, with clean lines and a balanced design under the open sky.

satellite/000427/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, structured outdoor area resembling a formal garden or courtyard complex. In the center, there is a long rectangular pool of still water, bordered by stone walkways and raised platforms. Surrounding the pool, there are multiple rows of small, evenly spaced plants, possibly flowers or shrubs, creating a symmetrical and ordered pattern. On the left side of the image, a tall, dark building with a flat roof stands in contrast to the open, light-colored space. The right side of the scene features more open areas with additional paths and low greenery. In the lower part of the photo, a line of dense trees runs horizontally, providing a natural border. The overall impression is one of calm precision and deliberate design. The lighting is even and bright, indicating a clear day with no visible clouds or shadows, suggesting fair and sunny weather. The image conveys a sense of stillness and careful planning.

satellite/000427/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex surrounded by paved areas and greenery. The central object is a multi-story structure with a rectangular shape, featuring many windows and a flat roof. The building has a clean, geometric design with a long, narrow extension on one side. To the left of the building is a parking lot with several cars parked in marked spaces. In front of the building, there is a well-maintained lawn area with trees and shrubs arranged in rows. On the right, a wide pathway or road runs parallel to the building, with a small open space nearby. The surrounding area includes additional greenery and a few smaller structures in the distance. The sky appears clear, and the daylight provides even lighting, suggesting it is a sunny day. The image has a calm and organized feel, typical of a well-planned urban or suburban area. The overall impression is one of order and functionality, with no signs of congestion or disarray. A few people can be seen walking near the building, adding a subtle sense of life to the scene. The color palette is neutral, with shades of gray, green, and beige dominating the view.

satellite/000428/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area with a prominent skyscraper on the left. The tall building has a dark glass facade and stands next to a wide open space filled with a patterned parking lot. To the right, there is a geometric series of structures with light-colored roofs, and a wide pathway cuts across the scene. The image appears to be taken on a cloudy day, with soft lighting and no strong shadows. The overall scene feels unoccupied and still, with no visible movement. The ground is mostly paved and organized, creating a sense of order and modern design. There are patches of green along the bottom edge, likely trees or shrubs, adding a small touch of nature. The atmosphere is calm and impersonal, typical of a planned city landscape.

satellite/000428/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large modern building complex with surrounding paved areas and green spaces. The central object is a tall rectangular structure with a dark, reflective facade, likely a commercial or office building, standing prominently on the left side of the frame. To the right and behind it is a massive open area composed of tiered rows of light-colored benches or seats, suggesting a stadium or public gathering space. A long, narrow water feature runs parallel to the seating area, bordered by concrete pathways. On the left, several smaller structures and parking lots are visible, organized in a grid. Trees line the bottom edge of the image and the top boundary, offering a contrast to the concrete landscape. The scene appears calm and orderly, with no visible people or vehicles. The sky is overcast, casting a soft, uniform light over the scene, which gives the image a neutral and slightly subdued atmosphere. The colors are mostly muted—grays, whites, and greens—enhancing the feeling of quiet functionality in an urban setting. There are no signs of rain or strong sun, contributing to the calm, still feeling of the environment.

satellite/000428/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex with a structured layout. The central object is a towering, dark-colored skyscraper with a rectangular shape, surrounded by lower-level structures that form a symmetrical arrangement. To the left of the main building, there is a smaller, lighter-colored building with flat roofs and open spaces, possibly used for support or storage. On the right side of the skyscraper, a terraced area with steps and repeating patterns creates a structured, geometric look, resembling a plaza or landscaped courtyard. The entire complex is bordered by wide, green-lined roads and paved pathways, suggesting careful urban planning. The scene appears clear and well-lit, indicating a sunny day with minimal clouds. The lack of visible people or moving vehicles gives the image a calm, still atmosphere, emphasizing order and precision. The overall impression is one of cleanliness, symmetry, and controlled design.

satellite/000429/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area. In the center stands a tall, dark rectangular building with a reflective surface, casting a long shadow. To its left, there are lighter-colored structures with flat roofs and open spaces, appearing more residential or commercial. On the right, a series of low buildings with patterned rooftops and a large gray parking structure are visible. The surrounding ground is paved, with patches of greenery at the bottom edge. The scene is captured under clear daylight, with strong shadows indicating midday sun. The overall impression is calm and structured, suggesting a quiet moment in a developed city area. The contrast between the dark building and the lighter surroundings creates a balanced but stark visual.

satellite/000429/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building complex with a distinct dark tower and surrounding structures. The central object is a tall, dark tower with a rectangular shape, standing out due to its dark color compared to the lighter buildings around it. To the left of the tower, there are several low-rise buildings with flat roofs and beige walls, some showing signs of construction or incomplete areas. On the right side, a curved, open-ended structure with a patterned design suggests a public space or entrance area. A paved road runs along the bottom of the image, bordered by green trees and shrubs, indicating a landscaped area. The overall scene has a clean, organized layout, with clear geometric patterns and open spaces. The lighting appears even and bright, suggesting a clear day with no clouds or fog. The image has a neutral, functional atmosphere, typical of urban or institutional architecture. There are no people or vehicles visible, giving the area a quiet and orderly feel.

satellite/000429/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, centered on a large dark building with a sleek, curved facade surrounded by open spaces. To the left of the building, there is a lower structure with a flat roof and several rectangular openings, possibly a parking or service area. On the right, a series of light-colored buildings with flat roofs and evenly spaced patterns suggest residential or commercial use. A narrow road runs along the bottom edge, flanked by green shrubs and small trees, providing a touch of nature amid the concrete. The sky is overcast, casting a soft, diffused light across the scene, which gives it a calm and quiet appearance. The absence of people or vehicles adds to the stillness of the environment. The overall layout appears ordered and designed with functionality in mind, creating a sense of balance between the built environment and open areas. The image captures a moment of quiet urban serenity.

satellite/000430/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural structure, likely an office or commercial building. The central object is a tall, dark rectangular tower with a reflective glass facade, standing prominently on the right side. To its left, a lighter-colored, multi-story building with a flat roof and large rectangular openings is visible. The buildings are surrounded by paved surfaces and a low wall with an outdoor staircase in the lower-left corner. The scene appears to be captured during overcast weather, with soft, diffused light casting minimal shadows. The atmosphere is neutral and quiet, lacking people or vehicles, suggesting a calm moment in an urban setting. The overall impression is one of clean lines and functional design, with no strong emotional cues.

satellite/000430/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural complex featuring large concrete structures and a prominent dark glass building. In the center of the image stands a tall, dark tower with smooth, reflective surfaces, contrasting with the surrounding lighter-toned buildings made of concrete and steel. To the left of the tower is a wide, flat-roofed structure with vertical panels, possibly a parking area or service block, and a narrow passage runs alongside it. On the right, another building displays a stepped design with multiple levels and a flat top, suggesting a public or institutional purpose. Lower sections of the complex include wheeled vehicles parked in open spaces, with leafy green trees lining the bottom edge, partially covering the base of the buildings. The scene is lit by bright, consistent sunlight, with clear skies and no clouds. The overall atmosphere feels structured and orderly, with little sign of human activity, giving the area a quiet yet functional appearance. The sharp angles and clean lines of the buildings create a sense of modernity and purpose, with the surrounding greenery offering a quiet contrast to the industrial feel.

satellite/000430/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a prominent modern high-rise building. The central structure is a tall, dark rectangular tower with a glass facade that reflects the sky, standing out among the surrounding low-rise buildings. To the left of the tower, there is a large open paved area with no clear activity, bordered by smaller structures and some fencing or railings. On the right, a series of low concrete buildings form a complex that includes what appear to be parking or storage spaces, with visible car shapes under shelter. The ground is mostly flat and paved, with patches of green trees lining the bottom edge, suggesting a landscaped border. The image is clear and well-lit, indicating it was taken on a bright, sunny day with no visible clouds or shadows cast by the sun. The overall impression is one of order and functional design, typical of a government or corporate campus, with a quiet and structured atmosphere.

satellite/000431/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a construction site surrounded by urban structures. In the center, there is a large, flat, concrete foundation with visible grid lines, suggesting preparation for building. To the left, partially covered materials and construction equipment are scattered, while a tall, dark structure stands to the right, possibly a building under development. The surrounding area appears built-up, with walls and pathways visible. The weather seems clear, with consistent lighting and no shadows indicating midday. The scene feels orderly yet incomplete, as if paused mid-progress. The overall impression is one of quiet, functional activity, with a sense of steady development rather than urgency.

satellite/000431/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban area with a mix of structures and open spaces. In the center is a large rectangular paved area, possibly a courtyard or parking lot, divided into sections by faint lines. Around it, various buildings with flat roofs are visible, some appearing older with worn surfaces. To the right, a tall dark structure stands out, possibly a modern building or a tower, contrasting with the more modest structures nearby. On the left, there is a row of long, low buildings with multiple windows, suggesting residential or commercial use. Near the bottom edge, a strip of green trees or bushes provides a natural border. The image is taken during the day under bright, even lighting, indicating clear weather with no signs of rain or fog. The overall impression is calm and orderly, with a sense of practical functionality rather than aesthetic design. There is no visible human activity, giving the scene a quiet and still atmosphere.

satellite/000431/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building complex in an urban area. The central object is a long, flat-roofed structure with a light-colored surface and visible rectangular sections, possibly storage areas or service bays, along its sides. The building has a modern, functional design with straight lines and no decorative features. To the right of the main structure is a taller, darker building with a grid-like facade, likely an office or residential tower. On the left, a parking lot with several vehicles is visible behind a low fence. In front of the building, a paved space with a patterned border and some green trees or shrubs provides a small amount of landscaping. The surrounding area includes roads and other buildings in the background, indicating a developed city setting. The weather appears clear and slightly overcast, with no shadows or bright sunlight. The overall view is calm and orderly, showing a typical scene of urban infrastructure.

satellite/000432/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, empty outdoor area, likely a training or exercise space. In the center, a rectangular concrete floor is visible, marked with faint grid lines. The space is enclosed on three sides by low concrete walls, while the left side is bordered by a tall, dark vertical surface, possibly a building or fence. On the far side, a smaller structure with a flat roof appears, possibly a shelter or control panel. A wooden fence runs along the front edge, separating the area from a patch of greenery below. The surface looks worn and unoccupied, with scattered debris and shadows casting across the ground. The image is taken in clear daylight, with bright sunlight highlighting the textures and lines. The scene feels calm and still, suggesting a place rarely used or temporarily unused.

satellite/000432/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large outdoor skating rink surrounded by a concrete structure. The rink is a square with a smooth, light-colored surface, possibly made of ice or a synthetic material, and is enclosed by a low wall on all sides. The square is bordered by a wide, gray concrete walkway that runs around its perimeter. To the left and right of the rink are flat, open areas that appear to be parking lots, with a few vehicles visible. In front of the rink, there is a low fence made of diagonal concrete slabs, and beyond that, a line of green trees runs along the bottom edge of the image. The surface of the rink shows some faint shadows, likely from nearby buildings or trees, and there are a few small structures or shelters along the back side. The lighting suggests it is a clear day with bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows. The overall mood is calm and still, with no people or activity visible, giving the scene a quiet and empty feel.

satellite/000432/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by roads and greenery. The main structure is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, appearing light gray or white, and it is covered by a large, open-sided pavilion supported by columns. Inside the pavilion, a few people and parked vehicles are visible. To the left of the building, a road runs vertically with a small car moving along it, while another road runs horizontally at the top of the image. On the right side, there are smaller structures and empty plots of land. In front of the main building, there is a neatly arranged row of trees and shrubs, creating a green border. The surrounding area includes paved pathways and parking spaces, some of which are occupied. The image appears to be taken on a clear day, with bright natural light casting short shadows. There is no sign of rain or fog, and the overall scene looks orderly and well-maintained. The atmosphere is calm and functional, suggesting a space designed for public or institutional use.

satellite/000433/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a large, flat-roofed building at the center, surrounded by paved surfaces and some greenery. To the left of the building, there is a curved road with a few visible vehicles and a smaller green space with trees. The building has a light gray surface and is bordered by what appears to be a low white wall or fence along its right edge. A modern, dark-colored structure with a slanted side stands to the left, possibly a bridge or overpass. The image shows no sign of people, and the overall scene appears calm and quiet. The lighting suggests a clear day with bright, even sunlight, producing minimal shadows and highlighting the clean, organized layout of the area. The atmosphere is neutral and orderly, with no indication of weather disturbances.

satellite/000433/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a parking lot and surrounding area. In the center of the image is a large, empty concrete parking lot marked with faint grid lines, likely a former or unused space. To the left of the parking lot is a curved road with a small, decorative roundabout, which includes a small tree and appears to be part of a landscaped area with greenery. A few cars are visible on the road near the roundabout. On the right side of the parking lot, a building with a dark roof and some covered sections can be seen, with what looks like a loading bay or garage entrance. A low wall with a patterned railing runs along the bottom edge of the image. The ground appears dry, and the shadows are sharp, suggesting the photo was taken on a sunny day. The overall scene is quiet and orderly, with a calm and still atmosphere. There are no people visible, and the scene gives a sense of quiet emptiness.

satellite/000433/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, open concrete area surrounded by roads and buildings. In the center of the picture is a wide, flat concrete field, possibly a parking lot or a large plaza, with some faint lines on its surface. To the left of this open field is a circular structure, resembling a small plaza or rotunda, with a curved walkway around it and green trees nearby. This structure is positioned next to a street where a few cars are visible. On the right side of the concrete field is a long, low-rise building with a series of windows and a flat roof. A small paved walkway or sidewalk runs along the bottom of the image, bordered by a line of neatly trimmed green trees. The surrounding area appears to consist of urban streets and small buildings. The image is taken on a clear day under bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows from the trees and structures. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no signs of heavy traffic or activity. The scene feels still and functional, typical of a developed city zone. There are no visible people or movement, adding to the quiet and structured feel of the area.

satellite/000434/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a prominent dark building on the left side. The building has a rectangular shape and appears to have a reflective surface. To the right, there is a large, lighter-colored open space with a grid-like pattern, possibly a plaza or parking lot. A curved road runs along the left edge of the image, with a few visible vehicles moving along it. Below the building, a row of green trees lines a pathway. The overall atmosphere is orderly and quiet, with clear visibility suggesting a sunny day. The scene has a clean and structured look, typical of city planning.

satellite/000434/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, showing a large rectangular building surrounded by paved surfaces and greenery. On the left side of the image is a curved road with a few vehicles visible, bordered by a low wall and some trees. The main structure, likely a public or commercial building, has a flat roof and is flanked by a darker high-rise tower on its left. To the right of the building is a wide expanse of paved space, possibly a parking lot or plaza, marked with faint lines. A wide road runs along the bottom of the image, separating the building area from a section with green trees, neatly lined in rows. Smaller patches of land, possibly gardens or landscaping, are seen in the lower left and bottom edges. The image appears to be taken on a clear day with bright, even lighting, creating sharp contrasts between the concrete, roads, and foliage. The overall scene feels orderly and structured, with a sense of calm urban planning. There are no signs of human activity, and the distant shadows suggest either morning or late afternoon light.

satellite/000434/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex and surrounding areas. The central object is a rectangular building with a flat roof, possibly a warehouse or industrial facility, featuring a dark vertical section on one side and a wide, light-colored courtyard or loading area in the middle. To the left of the building is a paved area with a curved road, a small parking space, and a person standing near a vehicle, suggesting light human activity. A green strip of trees runs along the bottom edge, separating the building from a field with geometric patterns, possibly farmland or empty lots. On the upper left, there is a wider road with vehicle movement, giving the image a sense of urban infrastructure. The lighting is even and clear, indicating a sunny day with no clouds, casting soft shadows and providing sharp visibility of the scene. The overall atmosphere is functional and calm, with little signs of bustling activity.

satellite/000435/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a mix of buildings and greenery. In the center, a large rectangular structure with a light-colored rooftop dominates the scene, surrounded by paved walkways and a low white fence. To the left, a tall dark building casts a long shadow across the ground, indicating sunny weather with clear skies. Along the bottom edge, a line of green trees and shrubs provides a natural contrast to the concrete and steel surroundings. The space appears clean and orderly, with a calm and structured atmosphere typical of a well-planned city district.

satellite/000435/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, open area surrounded by buildings and paved surfaces. In the center, there is a wide, flat concrete platform bordered by a fence made of metal bars arranged diagonally, giving it a geometric pattern. To the left of the platform stands a tall, dark building with many windows, while to the right, another structure with a lighter roof is visible. A road runs along the left edge of the image, with a narrow strip of green trees and bushes separating it from the platform. In the foreground, there are patches of grass and dirt, forming a grid-like pattern of small fields. The sky is overcast, with muted lighting that casts soft shadows, creating a calm and quiet atmosphere. The overall scene appears still and unpopulated, giving a sense of order and quiet urban planning, with no signs of movement or activity. The colors are mostly gray, brown, and green, with a neutral and functional tone.

satellite/000435/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban area centered around a prominent rectangular building with a flat roof and a light-colored exterior. The building has a tiered, stepped design along its front, resembling an open-air plaza or stage area, with cross-hatched patterns suggesting concrete or stone surfaces. To the left and right of the building, darker structures suggest other buildings or shaded areas, possibly with balconies or vertical elements. A paved road runs along the lower edge of the scene, bordered by a line of green trees that create a soft contrast with the hard concrete. The surrounding ground appears mostly barren with patches of light brown earth and faint white lines that could be markings or pathways. The overall scene is devoid of visible people or vehicles, giving it a quiet and somewhat vacant atmosphere. The image appears to have been taken on a clear day with bright, even lighting, casting minimal shadows and emphasizing the geometric layout of the structures and spaces. The lack of movement or activity contributes to a calm and still mood across the scene.

satellite/000436/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a large, light-colored building on the left and a smaller structure with a dark roof on the right. The building has a tiled or paneled facade and a flat roof, while the smaller structure has a solid, dark-colored upper section and a lighter lower part with a narrow vertical opening. A low, wall-like barrier runs in front of both structures, spaced along a straight line. In the foreground, green rectangular patches suggest a row of small bushes or ground cover, forming a thin green border across the bottom of the image. The overall scene is calm and orderly, with no people or moving vehicles visible. The lighting is even and neutral, suggesting a bright but overcast day.

satellite/000436/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a large paved space, likely a parking lot or plaza, bordered by buildings and greenery. The central object is a rectangular concrete area with faint grid lines, surrounded by walkways and low walls. To the left, a row of trees and plants runs along the edge, providing a green contrast to the gray pavement. On the right side, a dark, tall structure—possibly a building or parking garage—rises above the scene. Smaller structures and open spaces appear below the main lot, with some areas covered in dirt or gravel. The image is taken under clear daylight conditions, with bright, even lighting and no visible shadows indicating a midday sun. There is no sign of movement or people, giving the scene a still, quiet appearance. The overall atmosphere is neutral and functional, with no strong emotional tone, reflecting a typical city environment viewed from above.

satellite/000436/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by open spaces and greenery. The central object is a long rectangular building with a flat roof and a mix of light and dark sections, possibly indicating different materials or areas. The structure appears to have a courtyard or open area in the middle, enclosed by walls and bordered by smaller structures at the corners. To the left, a dense line of bushes or trees separates the building from a paved path. On the right, a taller structure with a darker facade stands adjacent to the main building, possibly a parking garage or an attached office wing. In front of the complex, there is a wide open ground area with patches of grass and dirt, intersected by narrow walkways. The scene is captured on a clear day with bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with a sense of quiet emptiness. No people or vehicles are visible, giving it a still and unclaimed feel. The image suggests a modern facility, possibly institutional or commercial, in a suburban or semi-urban setting.

satellite/000437/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with clean architectural lines. The central object is a tall structure with a dark facade, standing next to a lighter, rectangular building with large windows and flat walls. To the left, a low wall with horizontal slats borders a paved area, and above it, a grid of lighter walls creates a patterned layout. Green bushes form a neat line in front of the buildings, adding contrast. A narrow street or walkway runs at the bottom of the frame. The lighting is even and clear, suggesting a bright but overcast day. The scene appears orderly and functional, conveying a calm and uneventful urban environment.

satellite/000437/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a mix of buildings and paved spaces. In the center, there is a tall, dark rectangular building standing next to a lighter, flatter structure with a single visible doorway. To the left, a wide open space with a grid-like pattern of light-colored pavement appears to be a parking lot or plaza, bordered by a low fence-like design. On the right, another building with a flat roof and a lighter facade sits beside the main dark building. A narrow strip of green vegetation runs horizontally across the lower part of the image, separating the paved areas from a lower, bare earth section. The overall scene is clear, with bright daylight illuminating the structures and casting soft shadows, suggesting a calm, ordinary day. The image has a neutral, functional atmosphere with no signs of people or activity, emphasizing the clean, geometric layout of the environment.

satellite/000437/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a large, dark glass building on the right. The building has a tall, rectangular shape and reflects the sky, standing out against the lighter surrounding structures. To its left is a wide, light-colored paved area with visible cracks and patterns, possibly a parking lot or plaza. There are steps and ramps leading to the main building, suggesting public access. In front of the structures, a long line of green trees separates the buildings from a road, which appears to run horizontally across the lower part of the image. The sky is overcast, giving the scene a flat, gray light with no strong shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and functional, with the area appearing clean but unoccupied. The image shows a mix of concrete, glass, and greenery, typical of a city development in a quiet phase.

satellite/000438/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a tall, dark building surrounded by lighter structures. The central building has a sleek, vertical design and stands out due to its height and deep-colored facade. To its left, there is a lighter, rectangular building with a flat roof and an open space beneath it. Surrounding the buildings are paved areas, landscaped greenery, and rows of trees lining a road. On the right, a patterned walkway appears to lead toward the structures. The scene is captured under clear conditions, with bright, even sunlight casting soft shadows, indicating daytime. The overall atmosphere is calm and organized, typical of a planned city space, with a balance of construction and green landscape.

satellite/000438/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a tall, dark skyscraper at the center, standing out against lighter surrounding buildings. To the left of the skyscraper, there are lower structures with flat roofs and rectangular shapes, appearing in neutral gray and beige tones. On the right, more buildings with structured roofs and geometric designs are visible, suggesting a planned city layout. A green strip runs horizontally below the central cluster, likely a park or landscaped area with trees and shrubs lining a path. The textures of the streets and paved surfaces are visible, showing a mix of smooth concrete and patterned walkways. satellite/000465/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of built and natural elements. satellite/000465/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban area featuring a large rectangular building with a light-colored roof and dark walls, situated at the top right of the frame. satellite/000466/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a paved pathway and green landscaping. satellite/000466/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a rectangular paved space bordered by buildings and greenery. satellite/000466/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of buildings and open spaces. satellite/000467/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings, roads, and green spaces. satellite/000467/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban intersection. In the center, a paved road runs vertically, flanked by curved sidewalks and a row of green trees. satellite/000467/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with mixed green spaces and built structures. satellite/000468/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a paved road that curves through the scene. satellite/000468/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a park or green space in an urban area. satellite/000468/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection surrounded by a mix of green spaces and buildings. satellite/000469/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a landscaped area with paths and greenery. satellite/000469/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a suburban park area. satellite/000469/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of green spaces and buildings. In the center, a long, straight line of green trees separates a large paved area from two open fields with light brown soil and white curved pathways. The image was taken during the day under clear, bright conditions with strong sunlight, casting short shadows, and the overall view feels calm and orderly, with a focus on structured layout rather than natural beauty.

satellite/000470/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet rural landscape. In the center, a long dark pipe runs horizontally across the frame, surrounded by green bushes. satellite/000470/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a small building complex surrounded by farmland. Below, a large farm field is divided into sections by thin white paths, forming curved patterns across the brown soil. The field looks freshly tilled and flat, with no crops visible. To the lower left, patches of green vegetation suggest hedgerows or possibly nearby trees. There are no people or vehicles in sight. The sky is clear and bright, casting strong shadows on the ground, indicating sunlight during midday. The image feels quiet and open, with no signs of activity, highlighting the calm of rural life. The overall scene is simple and well-organized, reflecting typical agricultural planning.

satellite/000470/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with a mix of natural and man-made features. satellite/000471/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a large open space with a curved, light-colored path dividing two dirt fields. satellite/000471/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a large open field and a line of greenery. satellite/000471/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of natural and man-made elements. satellite/000472/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet, open area, likely a park or recreational space. satellite/000472/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a large, empty dirt field bordered by a white curving path on the right. satellite/000472/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park area with a modern building in the background. satellite/000473/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet outdoor area with a mix of natural and man-made elements. satellite/000473/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a landscaped area with a mix of natural and built features. satellite/000474/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a landscaped area near a large building. satellite/000474/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with paved pathways and landscaped green spaces. satellite/000475/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a landscaped area with a curved road and greenery. satellite/000475/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a landscaped urban area, likely a public park or plaza. satellite/000475/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a landscaped park and surrounding buildings. satellite/000476/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban intersection with a roundabout at its center. satellite/000476/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a paved urban intersection surrounded by green spaces and buildings. satellite/000476/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban intersection with a modern design. On the right side of the image, several buildings with flat roofs are visible, one of which has a dark façade. Above the buildings, a parking lot with rows of light-colored spaces can be seen. The area appears to be newly developed, with wide sidewalks and few people or vehicles. The lighting is bright and even, suggesting a clear day with sunlight. The overall view gives a clean, functional impression, somewhat detached and impersonal, as if captured from a high angle during a quiet moment.

satellite/000477/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city intersection with surrounding buildings and roads. In the center, a curved road leads into a roundabout with a small garden in the middle. satellite/000477/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban intersection with two roads meeting at a right angle. The overall scene is calm and orderly, with a sense of quiet structure and planning in the city layout. The light is bright but not harsh, giving the image a neutral and clean appearance.

satellite/000477/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban intersection with surrounding buildings and green spaces. On the bottom right, a building with a dark, flat roof occupies the lower corner. The scene is captured under clear, bright conditions with strong shadows, indicating midday sunlight. The image feels orderly and peaceful, presenting a standard city layout without signs of activity or congestion. The overall atmosphere is still and organized, emphasizing structure and geometry in the urban landscape.
